Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經有過一段時光\N{\fs13}There was a time above...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候\N{\fs13}A time before...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很完美\N{\fs13}There were perfect things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,猶若鑽石\N{\fs13}Diamond absolutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是世間萬物\N{\fs13}How things fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,都會隕落\N{\fs13}Things on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而隕落了的一切\N{\fs13}And what falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩少爺\N{\fs13} Master Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 已然不復 - 布魯斯\N{\fs13}- ... is fallen. - Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯斯 沒事的\N{\fs13}Bruce,it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯斯 別這樣\N{\fs13}Bruce, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠俠大戰超人 正義黎明\N終極版
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,正在上映\N佐羅的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亞瑟王神劍\N週三起映
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎\N{\fs13}Martha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在夢中 它們將我帶向光明\N{\fs13}In the dream they took me to the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一個美麗的謊言\N{\fs13}A beautiful lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,人類認識到了超人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 傑克 - 布魯斯\N{\fs13}- Jack. - Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,傑克 聽我說\N{\fs13}Jack, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你馬上讓所有人離開大樓\N{\fs13}I want you to get everyone out of the building. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白嗎 - 天吶\N{\fs13}- You understand? - My god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,遠離窗戶\N{\fs13}Stay away from the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 快 大家快走\N{\fs13}Let's go. Come on, start moving now, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 老闆要我們離開大樓\N{\fs13}Let's go. The boss wants us out of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都趕緊的\N{\fs13}So, let's make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,傑克 傑克\N{\fs13}Jack. Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 所有線路正忙\N{\fs13}We're sorry. All circuits are busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍後再撥\N{\fs13}Will you please try you call again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝\N{\fs13}Heavenly god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂與人間的創造者\N{\fs13}Creator of heaven and earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,寬恕我的靈魂吧\N{\fs13}Have mercy on my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,傑克\N{\fs13}JACK !!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大家牽好手\N{\fs13}Buddy hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看 真棒\N{\fs13}Everybody show me. Good job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快走\N{\fs13}Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,牽緊了\N{\fs13}Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs13}Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs13}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩先生 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}Mr. Wayne! Mr. Wayne!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腿沒知覺了\N{\fs13}I can't feel my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的腿沒知覺了 - 我們這裏需要人幫忙\N{\fs13}- I can't feel my legs. - We need help over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫我 我的腿沒知覺了\N{\fs13}Help me. I can't feel my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你會沒事的 聽見沒\N{\fs13}You're going to be okay, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沃萊士 他們怎麼叫你的 沃利?\N{\fs13}Wallace. What do they call you, Wally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老闆 你說了算\N{\fs13}You're the boss, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs13}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你會沒事的 - 小心 小心\N{\fs13}- You're going to be okay. - Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,來\N{\fs13}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶 我的腿沒知覺了\N{\fs13}Oh my god. I can't feel my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腿沒...沒知覺了\N{\fs13}I can't... I can't feel my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 你會沒事的\N{\fs13}It's okay. You're going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事的 好嗎\N{\fs13}You're okay, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 聽我說 我們會找到你媽媽的\N{\fs13}Okay, you know what? We're going to find your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fs13}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,18個月後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,印度洋某處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可口可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的風都不吉利\N{\fs13}All that wind is bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是血染長空之兆\N{\fs13}Blood in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她到了\N{\fs13}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲 內羅米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,萊恩小姐\N{\fs13}Miss Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,萊恩小姐 我是傑米·奧爾森 攝像師\N{\fs13}Miss Lane. Jimmy Olsen, photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 顯而易見 - 希倫在哪\N{\fs13}- Obviously. - Where's Heeron?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒能過境\N{\fs13}Uh. Trouble at the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼獲得許可的\N{\fs13}So uh. How'd you land it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這還是頭一回啊 阿瑪迦可從不接受採訪\N{\fs13}This is like pioneer stuff. Amajagh has never given an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道希倫跟我一起出任務時總說什麼嗎\N{\fs13}You know what Heeron always says when we are on assignment together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她都是閉嘴的\N{\fs13}Not a god damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡希倫\N{\fs13}I like Heron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs13}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,護照 電子器件 手機 相機\N{\fs13}Passports, electronics, phones, camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你們接頭的人說將軍准許拍照\N{\fs13}Your fixer said that the General approved photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是恐怖分子嗎 將軍\N{\fs13}Are you a terrorist, general?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他們沒告訴我做採訪的是位女士\N{\fs13}They did not tell me the interview was with a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是女士 我是記者\N{\fs13}I'm not a lady, I'm a journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我這個人 什麼都沒有\N{\fs13}What I am, is a man with nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只有對我人民的愛\N{\fs13}except a love of my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這些僱傭兵的開銷是誰出的 將軍\N{\fs13}Who's paying for these security contractors, general?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚在我們頭上飛過的無人機又是誰出的錢\N{\fs13}Who pays for the drones that passed over our heads at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一個問題總會引發另一個問題\N{\fs13}One question begs another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,對嗎\N{\fs13}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你要說什麼 將軍\N{\fs13}So what you're saying, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是台相機\N{\fs13}It's just a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,美國已聲明在你們國家的內戰中\N{\fs13}The United States has declared it's neutrality
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,保持中立 無論是政策上還是原則上\N{\fs13}in your country's civil war, both in policy and in principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,別打開...\N{\fs13}Oh, don't open...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,被你曝光了\N{\fs13}You just exposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這些虛偽的美式假話 說得像真理似的\N{\fs13}These pious American fictions...spoken like truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那是我的膠卷 我...\N{\fs13}Okay, that's my film. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,擁有權力的人既不會遵從\N{\fs13}Men with power obey neither
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,政策 也不會遵從原則 萊恩小姐\N{\fs13}policy nor principle , Miss Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,誰都一樣\N{\fs13}No one is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人是中立的\N{\fs13}No one... is neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,中情局\N{\fs13}CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在追蹤我們\N{\fs13}They're tracking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是中情局的\N{\fs13}You're CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麼 不是 不是的 - 你把他帶了過來\N{\fs13}- What?No,no! - You brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 他是個攝像師\N{\fs13}No!He's a photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,跟她無關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只是用她的身份做掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 露易絲\N{\fs13}It's okay, Lois.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,將軍 這事有解決的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我已被授權提議
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,利爪死了 長官\N{\fs13}Talon's down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,蟒蛇 我們失去了在場的線人 重複 我們失去了在場的線人\N{\fs13}Python, we've lost our asset on the ground. Repeat, we've lost our asset on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那個圍場裏還有平民 我們要救她出來\N{\fs13}There's still civilians in the compound. We'll extract her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 無人機即將進攻\N{\fs13}Negative. Rpa to engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,中止任務 然後藏好\N{\fs13}Stand down and get black.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸區會有友軍 所以...\N{\fs13}Well, there'll be friendlies in the blast zone. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,取消那該死的無人機\N{\fs13}Call off the god damn drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,中止任務 這是命令\N{\fs13}Stand down is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蟒蛇 - 行動\N{\fs13}- Python. - Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fs13}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不知道\N{\fs13}I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,無知和無辜\N{\fs13}Ignorance is not the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可不一樣 萊恩小姐\N{\fs13}as innocence. Miss Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,起來\N{\fs13}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來\N{\fs13}Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 他要來了\N{\fs13}Quickly, he's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,還有兩分鐘到達\N{\fs13}Inbound, 2 Mikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,飛過蟒蛇 快點\N{\fs13}Passing Python... Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,收隊\N{\fs13}Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 目標已鎖定 - 你可以開火了\N{\fs13}- Target locked. - You are clear to engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,導彈就緒 已在射程內\N{\fs13}Armed hot and in range.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,三\N{\fs13}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,二\N{\fs13}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一\N{\fs13}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,通訊連接被擊毀了\N{\fs13}Link's been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,被什麼擊毀的\N{\fs13}By what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你再走一步 就看她腦袋開花吧\N{\fs13}Take one step, you will see the inside of her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,村子裏的女人們聽到一種聲音\N{\fs13}The women in the village heard a noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就像天空裂開了似的\N{\fs13}Like the sky cracked open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他飛下來\N{\fs13}He came down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然後發生了交火\N{\fs13}then came fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.87,TOP,,0,0,0,,芬奇議員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,後來的事更可怕\N{\fs13}Even worse came after.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,政府進攻了\N{\fs13}The government attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在村中毫無憐憫可言\N{\fs13}No mercy in the villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父母都沒能逃過此劫\N{\fs13}My parents tried to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都只關注超人能做什麼\N{\fs13}The world has been so caught up with what Superman can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,卻沒人問他應該做什麼\N{\fs13}that... no one has asked what he should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,委員會將依此記錄向他追責\N{\fs13}Let the record show that this committee holds him responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他絕不會回應你們\N{\fs13}He'll never answer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會回應任何人\N{\fs13}He answers to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 甚至都不會回應上帝\N{\fs13}Not even I think, to god.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,58比0\N{\fs13}58 to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會再次打爆了哥譚\N{\fs13} Metropolis, again, blowing out Gotham city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,講真 只有死忠球迷還在看台上了\N{\fs13}Really, only the diehards are left in the stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,DC27 接到報警 哈勃威街1939號的空屋裏\N{\fs13}Delta Charlie 27. Reports of screams coming from vacant home
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有尖叫聲傳出\N{\fs13}at 1939 harborway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,湯姆 和你合作很棒\N{\fs13}Tom, it's been great working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:13.33,TOP,,0,0,0,,大都會州立大學隊 哥譚城市大學隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要感謝我們的監製和導播\N{\fs13}I want to thank our producer and director.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等下 - 我都不想指出...\N{\fs13}- Now wait a second. - I don't even want to suggest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DC27 請回答\N{\fs13}Delta Charlie 27, respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,單跪結束進攻吧\N{\fs13}Just take a knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他們排成一排了 克拉克森似乎要扔遠球\N{\fs13}They're lining up as if Clarkson is gonna throw it deep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不會吧 戴夫 - 要扔往端區了\N{\fs13}- Don't tell me, Dave. - Going to the end zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真沒必要這樣 - DC27\N{\fs13}- This is unnecessary. - Delta Charlie 27
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,齊克·貝克有空檔 貝克觸底接球得分\N{\fs13}Zeke Baker is open! Baker with a touch down catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信 我竟目睹了這一幕\N{\fs13}I can't believe I just watched that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,DC27 收到沒\N{\fs13}Delta Charlie 27. Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 我們這就去\N{\fs13}10- 4, we're on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,現在爆發了鬥毆\N{\fs13}And now a fight breaks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道哥譚市民是怎麼看他們的橄欖球隊的\N{\fs13}Gotham City, you know how they are about their football team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.23,TOP,,0,0,0,,大學橄欖球賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚這座城市不會太平\N{\fs13}Things could get ugly in the city tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:40.02,TOP,,0,0,0,,哥譚警局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:46.70,TOP,,0,0,0,,哥譚海港\N末日將至
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,化工廠\N{\fs14\shad0\bord1\fn黑体\c&HD2E9F0&\3c&HE2E2E2&\pos(341.757,140.99)}ACE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,上\N{\fs13}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.20,TOP,,0,0,0,,它救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:31.62,TOP,,0,0,0,,一個魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了\N{\fs13}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了 我們會幫忙\N{\fs13}It's okay. We're-We're going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是來幫忙的\N{\fs13}We're here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:38.92,TOP,,0,0,0,,它救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我們帶你們出去\N{\fs13}Okay, we're going to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎\N{\fs13}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.55,TOP,,0,0,0,,它還在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我聽不懂\N{\fs13}I - I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,請住手 請住手\N{\fs13}Please don't. Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fs13}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他是誰\N{\fs13}I don't know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他是誰\N{\fs13}I don't know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,該死\N{\fs13}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\fs13}Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到他了\N{\fs13}I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前從沒看到過 我不知道...\N{\fs13}I never saw him before. I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.91,0:23:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你差點打爛我的臉\N{\fs13}You almost took my face off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,能別朝好人開槍嗎\N{\fs13}How about you don't shoot the good guys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\fs13}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他給他烙了印\N{\fs13}He branded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:50.38,TOP,,0,0,0,,萊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.23,0:25:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嘿\N{\fs13}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.09,0:25:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想做飯呢 先給你個驚喜\N{\fs13}I was going to cook. Surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.85,0:25:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他們就發生的事舉行了聽證會\N{\fs13}They held hearings about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.81,0:25:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他們都在說... - 我不在乎\N{\fs13}- They're saying that... - I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.61,0:25:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎他們說什麼\N{\fs13}I don't care what they're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.40,0:25:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛的女人差點被炸或中槍\N{\fs13}The woman I love could have been blown up or shot
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.11,0:25:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想想可能的後果吧 - 想想已有的後果吧\N{\fs13}- Think of what could have happened. - Well, think about what did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.94,0:25:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人不是我殺的 如果他們是那麼想的話\N{\fs13}I didn't kill those men if that's what they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.86,0:25:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是那意思的話\N{\fs13}If that's what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.99,0:25:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是我想搞清楚發生了什麼\N{\fs13}I'm saying I want to understand what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.99,0:25:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是謝謝你救了我的命\N{\fs13}I'm saying, thank you for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.95,0:25:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是這是有代價的\N{\fs13}I'm saying there's a cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.76,0:25:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不知道可不可能\N{\fs13}I just don't know if it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.45,0:25:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道什麼可不可能\N{\fs13}Don't know what's possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.81,0:26:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,愛我的同時 做你自己\N{\fs13}For you to love me and be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.23,0:26:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 你會把公寓淹了的\N{\fs13}Clark, you're going to flood the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.42,0:27:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你還在工作?\N{\fs13}You still working?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.71,0:27:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾弗雷德 你老了 手腳也慢了\N{\fs13}You're getting slow in your old age, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.13,0:27:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,誰都會老 韋恩老爺\N{\fs13}It comes to us all, master Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.55,0:27:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,即便你老得沒機會英年早逝了\N{\fs13}Even you got too old to die young,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.01,0:27:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你也沒少為之嘗試\N{\fs13}and not for lack of trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.98,0:27:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,煙囪渡輪黃油塊 煙囪渡輪黃油塊\N{\fs13} Funnel-ferry butterbar. Funnel-ferry butterbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.27,0:27:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,煙囪渡輪黃油塊 煙囪渡輪...\N{\fs13} Funnel-ferry butterbar. Funnel-ferry...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.20,0:27:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,麥克風沒問題\N{\fs13}There's nothing wrong with the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有問題的是裝甲的新護層\N{\fs13}It's this new layer of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.82,0:27:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能重新裝線了\N{\fs13}I'll just have to rewire.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.24,0:27:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼\N{\fs13}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.95,0:27:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚有收穫嗎\N{\fs13}Last night was productive?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.16,0:27:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒\N{\fs13}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.20,0:27:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他級別太低 什麼都不知道\N{\fs13} He's too low level, he knew nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.46,0:27:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人倒知道些事\N{\fs13}This is a man who knows things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.46,0:27:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,阿納托裏·肯亞佐夫 他是俄國人\N{\fs13}Anatoli Knyazev. He's Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.34,0:28:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,生意遍佈全球 但他的基地就在哥譚港口\N{\fs13}Contracts all over the globe but he's base out of the port of Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.13,0:28:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,販賣武器和人口\N{\fs13}Weapons and human trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.01,0:28:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以理論上來說 白葡萄牙人是個俄國人\N{\fs13}So, the "White Portuguese" is a Russian, that's the theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.30,0:28:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.81,0:28:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,理論上來說 順著俄國人這條線 我能找到那個人\N{\fs13}The theory is that the Russian lead me to the man himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.77,0:28:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他真的是個人\N{\fs13}If he is indeed a him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.69,0:28:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你都不知道他是否存在 他可能是個幻影\N{\fs13}You don't even know if he exist. He could be a phantasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.65,0:28:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,幻影會想把一枚髒彈帶進哥譚?\N{\fs13}One that wants to bring a dirty bomb into Gotham?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.95,0:28:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那太危險了\N{\fs13}Ah, high-stakes round.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.24,0:28:28.13,TOP,,0,0,0,,哥譚自由報\N蝙蝠烙印下的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.37,0:28:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,新準則啊\N{\fs13}New rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.79,0:28:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是罪犯 阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}We're criminals, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.08,0:28:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直是罪犯 從沒變過\N{\fs13}We've always been criminals, nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.92,0:28:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,已經變了 先生\N{\fs13}Yes it has, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.51,0:28:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都已經變了\N{\fs13}Everything's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.89,0:28:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有人從天而降\N{\fs13}Men fall from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.06,0:28:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,諸神擲下雷電\N{\fs13}and gods hurl thunderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.39,0:28:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,無辜者喪命\N{\fs13}Innocents die.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.60,0:28:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,改變就是這麼開始的 先生\N{\fs13}That's how it starts,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.03,0:29:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,狂熱 憤怒 無能為力的感覺\N{\fs13}The fever, the rage, the feeling of... powerlessness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.20,0:29:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把好人變得\N{\fs13}that turns good men...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.30,0:29:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,殘暴\N{\fs13}cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.50,0:29:20.54,TOP,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,約翰 防守\N{\fs13} John, get d.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.93,0:29:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你們來了\N{\fs13}I did not know you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.22,0:29:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這就是招牌上的那個人啊 - 別當真\N{\fs13}- Man on the marquee. - Stop, don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.97,0:29:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親用他的名字命名了公司 他才是集團二字前的萊克斯\N{\fs13}My father named the company after himself. He was the Lex in front of the Corp.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.89,0:29:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 你好嗎 - 好極了\N{\fs13}- Hi, how are you doing? - Oh, really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.98,0:29:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好極了?不錯 不錯\N{\fs13}Really great? Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.98,0:29:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\fs13}Uh. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.97,0:29:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸為了吸引投資人 就開始說\N{\fs13}No, uh, Dad started saying that he named
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.10,0:29:37.77,TOP,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.23,0:29:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他是用孩子的名字給公司命名的\N{\fs13}the company after his kid at investor pitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.47,0:29:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那些老富婆 她們覺得這做法很可愛\N{\fs13}Rich old ladies. They thought it was very cute, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.86,0:29:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都說 為萊克斯開支票吧\N{\fs13}"Write check for Lex."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.49,0:29:44.94,TOP,,0,0,0,,已解鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.55,0:29:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸在東德出生\N{\fs13}You know, Dad was born in east Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.80,0:29:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他是吃變質餅乾長大的\N{\fs13}He grew up eating uh... stale crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.21,0:29:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,每隔一個週六 他就得列隊行軍\N{\fs13}And every other Saturday, he had to march in a parade
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.46,0:29:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,向獨裁者揮舞鮮花\N{\fs13}and waved flowers at tyrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.56,0:29:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我認為這是天意 他的兒子\N{\fs13}So, I think it was providence that his son,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.86,0:29:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我 最終得到了這個\N{\fs13}me, would end up with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.80,0:30:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一個大都會重建組員找到的\N{\fs13}One of my rebuild Metropolis crews found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.38,0:30:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,來自氪星人世界引擎的一個小紀念品\N{\fs13}A little souvenir from the Kryptonian World Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一塊石頭和國家安全有什麼關係\N{\fs13}What's a rock have to do with Homeland Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.47,0:30:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,國家安全?\N{\fs13}Homeland Security?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.99,0:30:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 女士 是星球安全\N{\fs13}No, no, no... ma'am. Planetary Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.06,0:30:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這個碎塊是放射性外太空礦物\N{\fs13}The fragment is of a radio active Xeno mineral
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.56,0:30:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我們懷疑它或許有生物交互作用\N{\fs13}We suspected it might have bio interactions,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.01,0:30:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我們把樣本給了陸軍傳染病醫學研究所\N{\fs13}so, we took the sample to amriid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.43,0:30:19.17,TOP,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.31,0:30:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏保留著氪星死者的遺體\N{\fs13}Where they keep the remains of the Kryptonian decedent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.84,0:30:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,當我們將這個礦物接觸佐德將軍時\N{\fs13}And, when we exposed general Zod to the mineral,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.27,0:30:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了這樣的情況\N{\fs13}this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.97,0:30:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,強烈的生物降解作用 ​​在衰變氪星人的細胞\N{\fs13}Profound biodegradation, decaying Kryptonian cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.53,0:30:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們斷定 如果找到一個足夠大的樣本 就能武器化這種礦物\N{\fs13}We concluded the mineral could be weaponized, if a large enough sample was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.75,0:30:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,後來 在魚群中 一個大傢伙\N{\fs13}And then, among the fishes, a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.56,0:30:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,躺在印度洋的海底\N{\fs13}Lying at the bottom of the Indian Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.32,0:30:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,猶如翡翠城\N{\fs13}Emerald City.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.87,0:30:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,美極了\N{\fs13}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.28,0:30:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這大石頭有放射性\N{\fs13}Now, Rocky is radio active, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.23,0:30:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,需要你們的一張進口許可證\N{\fs13}what he needs from you is an import license.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.49,0:30:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我們為什麼要武器化這種物質\N{\fs13}And why would we want to weaponize this material?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.27,0:30:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用來威懾 預備一顆銀彈\N{\fs13}As a deterrent. A silver bullet to keep in reserve
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.31,0:31:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來對付氪星人 女士 這樣你的後輩\N{\fs13}to use against the Kryptonians. So, the day doesn't come, Madame,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.05,0:31:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在檢閱台上揮舞雛菊的日子就不會到來\N{\fs13}when your children are waving daisies at a reviewing stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.61,0:31:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,據我所知 那些氪星人中\N{\fs13}Last I looked, the only one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.21,0:31:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,還在天上飛來飛去的只有超人\N{\fs13}flying around up here was Superman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.11,0:31:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 超人\N{\fs13}Ha. Yes, Superman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.80,0:31:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 但還有...還有更多這一類的\N{\fs13}Yeah, but, there are... there are more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.66,0:31:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 超人類論 - 沒錯 超人類論\N{\fs13}- The meta- human thesis. - Yes, the meta- human thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.16,0:31:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這些超常之人很可能生活在我們之中\N{\fs13}More likely than not. These exceptional beings live among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.69,0:31:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們眾多神話的基礎 就是我們...\N{\fs13}The bases of our myths. Gods among men upon our...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.51,0:31:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們小藍星上的人間諸神\N{\fs13}our little blue planet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.21,0:31:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是非得用銀彈\N{\fs13}You don't have to use the silver bullet,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.29,0:31:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 如果鑄造一顆\N{\fs13}but, if you forge one...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.65,0:31:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼\N{\fs13}Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.11,0:31:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就不用依賴怪物們的仁善了\N{\fs13}We don't have to depend upon the kindness of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.30,0:31:36.72,TOP,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.43,0:31:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能互相幫助\N{\fs13}There're ways we can help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.23,0:31:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到我這邊的辦公處來吧\N{\fs13}Would you step into my office here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.40,0:31:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs13}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.78,0:31:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼需求\N{\fs13}What's your wish list?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.41,0:31:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,進入墜毀的氪星飛船殘骸\N{\fs13}Access to the wreck of the crashed Kryptonian ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.37,0:32:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,成交\N{\fs13}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:20.53,TOP,,0,0,0,,保持通暢\N自動門
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.27,0:32:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,還要那個外星人的完整遺體 用於測試\N{\fs13}The complete remains of the dead alien for testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.09,0:32:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要佐德的屍體?\N{\fs13}You want Zod's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.47,0:32:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.78,0:33:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻桃味的\N{\fs13}It's cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.52,0:33:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是時候\N{\fs13}Because the time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.56,0:33:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,讓全世界聽到另一種聲音了\N{\fs13}for the world to hear the other side of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.56,0:33:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人們說這個超人是一位英雄 好吧 可又是誰的英雄呢\N{\fs13}They say this Superman is a hero. Okay, but whose hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.82,0:33:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,假如超人現在就在這裏\N{\fs13}If Superman were here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.03,0:33:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你想對他說什麼\N{\fs13}What would you want to say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.20,0:33:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對他說 我的家人也有夢想\N{\fs13}That my family too had dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.32,0:34:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,並看著他的雙眼\N{\fs13}To look him in his eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.49,0:34:03.16,TOP,,0,0,0,,採訪卡希納·澤瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.21,0:34:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,問他是如何判定\N{\fs13}and ask him how he decides
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.50,0:34:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哪些生命有價值\N{\fs13}which lives count
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.45,0:34:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哪些生命沒有價值\N{\fs13}and which ones do not?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.37,0:34:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,星球日報 超人阻止了導彈攻擊\N超人英勇營救
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.37,0:34:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯斯·韋恩營救員工\N一男子被首席執行官從廢墟中救出
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.13,0:34:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄們
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.63,0:35:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 下來\N{\fs13}Sir. Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.66,0:35:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 我說了 下來 快點\N{\fs13}Sir, I said, get down, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.30,0:35:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這裏能要些支援嗎\N{\fs13}Can we get some backup here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.90,0:35:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 住手\N{\fs13}Hey. Hey. Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.23,0:35:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs13}HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.67,0:35:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,露易絲 罪證化驗室 三號線\N{\fs13}Lois. Crime Lab, on 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.88,0:35:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是萊恩\N{\fs13}This is Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.80,0:35:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,肯特 今天你負責體育版\N{\fs13}Kent, you're sports today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.72,0:35:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你去哥譚 跟進橄欖球方面的消息\N{\fs13}I want you to go over to Gotham, follow up on the football.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.47,0:35:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,弱旅夢碎 哥譚與榮耀 相隔10碼\N{\fs13}"Underdog dreams dashed: Ten yards between Gotham and glory."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.81,0:35:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在哥譚自己當心點\N{\fs13}Watch yourself over there at Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.56,0:35:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓人搶了你的午餐錢\N{\fs13}Don't let them take your lunch money.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.97,0:35:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你們在看這個嗎\N{\fs13}Hey. Are you guys watching this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.67,0:35:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,緊急救援人員在英雄公園周圍快速設防\N{\fs13}Emergency responders quickly created a precautionary perimeter around Heroes Park
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.65,0:36:00.86,TOP,,0,0,0,,英雄公園發生仇恨犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.93,0:36:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,同時將此男子從這座受人愛戴的紀念碑上帶走\N{\fs13}while they brought the man down from this beloved monument.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.87,0:36:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌疑人已被確認是沃萊士·弗農·基夫\N{\fs13}The suspect has been identified as Wallace Vernon Keefe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.20,0:36:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我為布魯斯·韋恩工作 我為布魯斯·韋恩工作\N{\fs13}I work for Bruce Wayne! I work for Bruce Wayne!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.20,0:36:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他將受到故意破壞公物及拒捕的指控\N{\fs13}There'll be arraign on charges of vandalism, resisting arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.70,0:36:16.38,TOP,,0,0,0,,偽神
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.57,0:36:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,並受到一項製造恐怖威脅的重罪指控\N{\fs13}and a felony charge of making terrorist threats
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.33,0:36:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這些將導致多達40年的監禁\N{\fs13}that carries up to 40 years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.59,0:36:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐的蠢貨\N{\fs13}Poor son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.51,0:36:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會8台新聞報道\N{\fs13}Metropolis news 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.67,0:36:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,珍妮\N{\fs13}Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.93,0:36:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,頭條\N{\fs13}Headline:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.97,0:36:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對空中飛人的強烈好感結束了 問號\N{\fs13}"End of love affair with man in the sky, question mark."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.18,0:36:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.05,0:37:04.76,TOP,,0,0,0,,哥譚警局
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.98,0:37:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她在嗎\N{\fs13}Is she in?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.94,0:37:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她已經離開了\N{\fs13}Oh, she's been gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.73,0:37:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她幹什麼了 警官\N{\fs13}What'd she do, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.52,0:37:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是警察 我是記者\N{\fs13}Oh, I'm not a cop. I'm a reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.24,0:37:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,住這裏的這位年輕女士...\N{\fs13}The young lady living here...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.11,0:37:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她一直沒回來\N{\fs13}Uh, she hasn't been back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.82,0:37:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她要是聰明 就已經離開這座城市了\N{\fs13}In fact, if she's smart, then she's got out of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.24,0:37:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而你得在天黑前離開這裏\N{\fs13}And you need to get out of here... before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.04,0:37:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 除非你想撞見他 - 別聽他的鬼話\N{\fs13}- Unless you want to run into him. - Don't listen to that nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.46,0:37:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那些做虧心事的人才害怕他\N{\fs13}Only people scared of him, people who got reason to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.29,0:37:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕誰\N{\fs13}Scared of who?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.55,0:37:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他的狠辣已不同往日\N{\fs13}Well, there's a new kind of mean in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.01,0:37:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他很憤怒\N{\fs13}He is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.39,0:37:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他正在狩獵\N{\fs13}And he's hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.56,0:37:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他們看看你的厲害\N{\fs13} Show 'em what you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.10,0:37:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 加油\N{\fs13}Let's go!Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.06,0:37:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快出拳\N{\fs13}Throw a punch, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.27,0:38:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 加油\N{\fs13}Let's go! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.23,0:38:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.37,0:38:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這地方把運氣當成一種侮辱\N{\fs13}The house treats luck like an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.53,0:38:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人的好運總會是他兄弟的厄運\N{\fs13}Good luck for one is always his brother's misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.98,0:38:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但所有的帳最後都要結平
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.40,0:38:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和一個波修瓦劇院的芭蕾舞女共度了三晚 她只教了我這一句\N{\fs13}3 nights with a Bolshoi ballerina, that line was all she taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.70,0:38:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不只這一句\N{\fs13}Not all I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.03,0:38:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上愉快\N{\fs13}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.91,0:38:59.98,TOP,,0,0,0,,設備克隆成功
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.04,0:38:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這是恐怖的獨裁統治\N{\fs13}It's like a one man reign of terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.07,0:39:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這個蝙蝠義警一直在盯著港口\N{\fs13}This bat vigilante has been consistently targeting the port
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.96,0:39:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,還有鄰近的工程和廉價公寓\N{\fs13}and the adjacent projects and tenements.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.80,0:39:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看來 那些警察其實是在幫他\N{\fs13}And as far as I can tell the cops are actually helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.00,0:39:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哥譚的犯罪浪潮\N{\fs13}"Crime wave in Gotham."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.85,0:39:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,其他爆炸性新聞 水是濕的\N{\fs13}Other breaking news: "Water, wet."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.03,0:39:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 橄欖球的報道寫好了嗎 - 我們為什麼不報道這個\N{\fs13}- Did you file the football yet? - Why aren't we covering this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.47,0:39:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因為窮人不買報紙?\N{\fs13}Poor people don't buy papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.37,0:39:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,人們都不買報紙了 就是這樣 肯特\N{\fs13}People don't buy papers, period, Kent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.30,0:39:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,佩裏 你分派報道時 就是在選擇誰重要\N{\fs13}Perry, when you assign a story, you're making a choice about who matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.73,0:39:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 誰值得 - 終於醒了啊 斯莫維爾土包\N{\fs13}- and who's worth it. - Good morning, Smallville.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.87,0:39:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,美國的良心已隨羅伯特 馬丁和約翰一起死了\N{\fs13}The American conscience died with Robert, Martin and John.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.00,0:39:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉\N{\fs13}Sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.73,0:39:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有匹配的\N{\fs13}No match.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.04,0:39:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我在罪證化驗室的人都沒見過這個\N{\fs13}My guys in the crime lab, never seen one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.79,0:39:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這叫子彈 開槍打人用的\N{\fs13}It's called a bullet. You shoot people with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.96,0:39:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,從沙漠的交火現場回收的\N{\fs13}Recovered from the scene of the fire fight in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.71,0:39:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界任何地方都沒有商業買賣 連黑市也沒\N{\fs13}Not sold anywhere commercially in the world, even black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以?\N{\fs13}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.00,0:39:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是誰把原型軍用子彈給了在撒哈拉的圖阿雷格戰士\N{\fs13}So, who gave prototype military rounds to tuareg fighters in the Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.14,0:39:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是記者 你來告訴我\N{\fs13}You are the reporter, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.22,0:39:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為美國政府在宣稱支持民選政府的同時\N{\fs13}I think the U.S government is arming the rebels
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也在給反叛軍提供武裝\N{\fs13}while claiming to support the elective government.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.68,0:40:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,直接說想幹嘛 露易絲\N{\fs13}The ask, Lois.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.60,0:40:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚飛華盛頓 在那待幾天\N{\fs13}Flight to DC tonight, a couple of days there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.20,0:40:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs13}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.37,0:40:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,普通經濟艙 不准選大空間座位\N{\fs13}Coach. No extra leg room.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.93,0:40:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,豪華經濟艙\N{\fs13}Economy plus.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.30,0:40:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,普通經濟艙\N{\fs13}Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.63,0:40:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼沒告訴我\N{\fs13}So, why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.64,0:40:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在引蛇上身 小露\N{\fs13}You're digging up snakes, Lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.40,0:40:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這有點危險\N{\fs13}It's kinda dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.23,0:40:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才沒告訴你\N{\fs13}That's why I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.21,0:40:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,萊恩 你不是要趕飛機嗎\N{\fs13}Lane, don't you have a plane to catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.73,0:40:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 頭\N{\fs13}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.47,0:40:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會圖書館的公益活動\N{\fs13}Benefit for the Library of Metropolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.65,0:40:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,委員會有人請求克拉克·肯特報道這件事\N{\fs13}Someone on the committee requested that Clark Kent cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是某個做慈善的醜老太婆喜歡呆子\N{\fs13}Probably some old charity crone has got a thing for nerds.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.40,0:40:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,議員\N{\fs13}Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.78,0:40:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,午餐前喝點波旁酒嗎\N{\fs13}Little bourbon before lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.53,0:40:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我司機在外面 我不能久留\N{\fs13}My driver's outside, I can't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.45,0:41:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不喝波旁酒? 你這樣的肯塔基姑娘竟然不喝?\N{\fs13}No bourbon? A Kentucky girl like yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.53,0:41:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸總說\N{\fs13}My dad always said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.29,0:41:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,肯塔基麥芽漿是健康的秘訣\N{\fs13}Kentucky mash was the secret to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.17,0:41:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這曾是他的房間\N{\fs13}This was his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.20,0:41:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直保持著原樣\N{\fs13}I kept it just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我把一切都保持原樣的話 或許有一天我爸會回來\N{\fs13}"Maybe one day dad'll come back if I just keep everything the same."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.48,0:41:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這真傻\N{\fs13}That is silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.10,0:41:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,孤兒的妙想天開\N{\fs13}The magical thinking of orphan boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.77,0:41:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會給你的礦物批准進口許可證\N{\fs13}I'm blocking the import license for your mineral.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.99,0:41:48.04,TOP,,0,0,0,,注:改自"The redcoats are coming"\N美國獨立戰爭期間 保羅·列維爾喊出的英軍來襲警報
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.00,0:41:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,紅披風要來了\N{\fs13}The Red Capes are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.40,0:41:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,紅披風要來了\N{\fs13}The Red Capes are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.80,0:41:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你聽證會的人\N{\fs13}You and your hearings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.17,0:42:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在街上飛奔 來警告我們\N{\fs13}Galloping through the streets to warn us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.00,0:42:06.20,TOP,,0,0,0,,注:改自亨利·沃茲沃斯·朗費羅的讚美詩《保羅·列維爾騎馬來》\N原為"One,if by land,two,if by sea"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.00,0:42:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,從陸地來掛一盞燈 從天上來掛兩盞燈\N{\fs13}One, if by land. Two, if by air.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.03,0:42:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,議員 你知道美國最古老的謊言嗎\N{\fs13}Do you know the oldest lie in America, Senator?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.47,0:42:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能叫你瓊嗎 - 你喜歡怎麼叫都行\N{\fs13}- Can I call you June? - You can call me whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.97,0:42:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也能把一桶尿叫做奶奶的蜜桃茶\N{\fs13}Take a bucket of piss and call it Granny's peach tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.40,0:42:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把一件暗殺武器叫做威懾\N{\fs13}Take a weapon of assassination and call it deterrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.50,0:42:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙不了我\N{\fs13}You won't fool a fly on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.80,0:42:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會上當\N{\fs13}I'm not going to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.53,0:42:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 如果我就改變了這房裏的\N{\fs13}Hey, you don't think Dad would mind, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.30,0:42:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一件東西\N{\fs13}If I change just...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.00,0:42:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我爸是不會介意的吧\N{\fs13}... just one thing in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.07,0:42:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那東西應該是顛倒過來的\N{\fs13}Because that should be upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.70,0:42:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我們更清楚了 對嗎\N{\fs13}Now, we know better now, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.93,0:42:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,魔鬼並非來自我們下方的地獄\N{\fs13}The devils don't come from hell beneath us. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.83,0:43:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他們來自天上\N{\fs13}No, they come from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.77,0:43:39.20,TOP,,0,0,0,,瑪莎·韋恩
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.60,0:45:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望韋恩家族的下一代不會繼承一座空酒窖\N{\fs13}I hope the next generation of Waynes won't inherit an empty wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.53,0:45:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,說得可能會有下一代似的\N{\fs13}Not that there's likely to be a next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.04,0:45:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 先生\N{\fs13}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.03,0:45:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這是那個俄國人手機上打出的所有電話\N{\fs13}This is every call made from the Russian's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.59,0:45:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有兩通提到了與白葡萄牙人的生意\N{\fs13}Two mentions of business with the "White Portuguese" and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.51,0:45:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,並且在繼續向亞歷山大·盧瑟的私人住所\N{\fs13}it's continuing transmitting blacked-out data to the personal residence
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.12,0:45:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,傳輸隱蔽數據\N{\fs13}of Alexandra Luthor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.54,0:45:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你認為萊克斯·盧瑟就是白葡萄牙人?\N{\fs13}You think Lex Luthor is the "White Portuguese"?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.36,0:45:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不出他需要進口武器來賺錢\N{\fs13}I can't see that he needs the income from imported arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.24,0:45:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何 我得在他的房子裏放個竊錄器\N{\fs13}Regardless, I'll need to put a leech at his house,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.60,0:45:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我還需要戰衣\N{\fs13}and I'm going to need the suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.73,0:45:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠審問了六個人 卻一無所獲\N{\fs13}The Bat interrogated 6 people and came away with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.38,0:45:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是布魯斯·韋恩搞到了信息\N{\fs13}It was Bruce Wayne that got the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.89,0:45:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯斯·韋恩可沒法闖進萊克斯·盧瑟的房子\N{\fs13}Well, Bruce Wayne can't break into Lex Luthor's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.91,0:45:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯斯·韋恩不用闖進去\N{\fs13}Bruce Wayne won't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.62,0:45:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經被邀請了\N{\fs13}He's been invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.83,0:45:57.13,TOP,,0,0,0,,敬請參加 11月1日晚上7點\N由亞歷山大·盧瑟舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.73,0:46:23.44,TOP,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 你是個笑話 蝙蝠俠
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.15,0:47:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拍張照 - 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}- Have a shot. - Mr. Wayne!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.11,0:47:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊\N{\fs13}Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.57,0:47:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰\N{\fs13}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.44,0:47:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定沒聽過讓他們吃蛋糕的梗\N{\fs13}You must be new to the "let them eat cake" beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.87,0:47:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是布魯斯·韋恩\N{\fs13}That is Bruce Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.63,0:47:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有請慈善家 藏書家\N{\fs13}Philanthropist. Bibliophile.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.20,0:47:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會圖書館的真朋友 萊克斯·路瑟先生致辭\N{\fs13}True friend of the Library of Metropolis. Mr. Lex Luthor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.30,0:47:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我? 好吧\N{\fs13}Me? Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.54,0:47:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,尼基\N{\fs13}Nicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.89,0:47:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我為難了\N{\fs13}You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.13,0:47:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,演講 演講 這個那個\N{\fs13}Speech. Speech. Uh, blah blah blah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.79,0:47:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,酒水免費\N{\fs13}Open bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.07,0:47:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,演講結束\N{\fs13}The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.24,0:47:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,慈善家這個詞 源於希臘文\N{\fs13}The word "philanthropist" comes from the Greek.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.13,0:47:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是博愛之人\N{\fs13}Meaning a lover of humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.28,0:47:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,約2500年前被創造的\N{\fs13}It was coined about 2,500 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.41,0:47:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我要往哪走 阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}Alright, where am I going, Alfred?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.96,0:47:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,走過電梯 往左\N{\fs13}Go past the elevator.Do a left.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.19,0:47:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 一定是\N{\fs13} That's right, must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.25,0:48:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在地下室的服務通道\N{\fs13}It's in the service corridor in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.54,0:48:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,走下樓\N{\fs13}Go down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.67,0:48:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,神明與人類之間\N{\fs13} Gods and men.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.30,0:48:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,普羅米修斯選擇了我們\N{\fs13}Prometheus went with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.56,0:48:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他破壞了宙斯毀滅人類的計劃\N{\fs13}and he ruined Zeus' plan to destroy man kind
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.34,0:48:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為此 他遭到了雷劈\N{\fs13}and for that, he was given a thunderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.70,0:48:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎很不公平\N{\fs13}Hm. That seems unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.25,0:48:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,言歸正傳 大都會圖書館...\N{\fs13}On the serious note, the Library of Metropolis...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.29,0:48:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,走到你進來時看到的樓梯那 下樓\N{\fs13}Go to the stairs. You saw them on your way in. Down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.73,0:48:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但曾有一段時間 我爸買不了\N{\fs13}But at one time, Dad could not buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.28,0:48:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我父親小時候買不起書\N{\fs13}No, My father could not afford books growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.48,0:48:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他不得不從垃圾桶裏翻出昨天的報紙\N{\fs13}He had to root through the garbage for yesterday's newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.28,0:48:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你右邊是廚房\N{\fs13}All right. You got the kitchens on your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.96,0:48:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,往左\N{\fs13} Do a left.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.45,0:48:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你前面 就是你要去的地方\N{\fs13}Right in front of you, that's where you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.67,0:48:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,需要幫忙嗎 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}May I help you, Mr. Wayne?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.95,0:48:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是...以為洗手間在這下面\N{\fs13}Uh, I just... thought the bathroom was down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.69,0:48:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定是...\N{\fs13}I must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.94,0:49:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,最後一杯馬提尼量太多了\N{\fs13}That last Martini was two too many, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.71,0:49:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 男洗手間在樓上 - 太好了 我沒事\N{\fs13}- Men's room is upstairs. - Great, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.56,0:49:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡那雙鞋\N{\fs13}I like those shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.74,0:49:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能待在下面 阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}I can't stay down here, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.95,0:49:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,上樓交際去\N{\fs13}Go upstairs and socialize.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.33,0:49:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,找個大都會的年輕女士娶回家\N{\fs13}Some young lady from Metropolis will make you honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.80,0:49:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,別做夢了 阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}In your dreams, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.26,0:49:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,書本就是知識 知識就是力量\N{\fs13}Books are knowledge, and knowledge is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.66,0:49:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而我... 不...\N{\fs13}And I am... Heh heh heh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.84,0:49:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fs13}I, umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.98,0:49:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我是什麼 我在說什麼呢\N{\fs13}No, what am I? What was I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.28,0:49:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.22,0:49:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,人苦樂參半的悲哀就在於有知識卻無力量\N{\fs13}The bittersweet pain among men is having knowledge with no power.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.70,0:49:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為...\N{\fs13}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.41,0:49:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因為二者互相矛盾 還有...\N{\fs13}Because that is paradoxical, and umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.80,0:49:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝各位光臨\N{\fs13}Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.44,0:49:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,請盡情暢飲\N{\fs13}Please drink. Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.95,0:50:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩先生 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}Mr. Wayne. Mr. Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.63,0:50:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我是克拉克·肯特 星球日報的\N{\fs13}Clark Kent, Daily Planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.04,0:50:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的基金會已發佈了支持圖書公益的聲明\N{\fs13}Oh, my foundation has already issued a statement in support of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.13,0:50:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先生?\N{\fs13}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.63,0:50:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,美女一來 品行就敗 別引用這句話 好嗎\N{\fs13}Pretty girl. Bad habit. Don't quote me, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.97,0:50:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你對哥譚的蝙蝠義警持什麼立場\N{\fs13}What's your position on the bat vigilante in Gotham?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.80,0:50:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,星球日報\N{\fs13}Daily Planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.83,0:50:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 這是我旗下的 還是其他人的\N{\fs13}Wait.Do I own this one? Or is that the other guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.06,0:50:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,公民自由權已在你的城市中被踐踏\N{\fs13}Civil liberties has been trampled on in your city.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.93,0:50:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,善良的人生活在恐懼之中\N{\fs13}Good people living in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.44,0:50:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要相信你聽到的一切流言 孩子\N{\fs13}Don't believe everything you hear, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.47,0:50:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是我親眼所見 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}I've seen it, Mr. Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.67,0:50:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他認為他在法律之上\N{\fs13}He thinks he's above the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.87,0:50:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,星球日報竟在批評那些自認為在法律之上的人\N{\fs13} The daily planet criticizing those who think they're above the law
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.13,0:50:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有點虛偽啊 你不覺得嗎\N{\fs13}is a little hypocritical, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.33,0:50:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而每次你們的英雄從樹上救下一隻貓\N{\fs13}Considering every time your hero saves a cat out of a tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.20,0:50:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就會寫一篇吹捧的社論 來報道一個...\N{\fs13}you write a puff piece editorial, about an alien who...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.54,0:50:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要想摧毀整個星球 就能做到的外星人\N{\fs13}if he wanted to, could burn the whole place down.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.83,0:50:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真到那時 我們做什麼都無法阻止他\N{\fs13}There wouldn't be a damn thing we can do to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.87,0:51:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上大多數人並不贊同你的看法 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}Most of the world doesn't share your opinion, Mr. Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.27,0:51:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是我心中的哥譚市影響了我 我們只是...\N{\fs13}Maybe it's the Gotham city in me, we just...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.39,0:51:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,和穿得像小丑的怪胎們有過一段糟糕的歷史\N{\fs13}... have a bad history with freaks dressed like clowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.48,0:51:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夥計們 布魯斯·韋恩和克拉克·肯特相見了\N{\fs13}Boys! Mm, Bruce Wayne meets Clark Kent.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.18,0:51:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡 我喜歡把人們聚到一起\N{\fs13}Ah, I love it! I love bringing people together!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.03,0:51:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你們好啊 - 萊克斯\N{\fs13}- How are we? - Lex.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.23,0:51:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 很好 嗨 你好\N{\fs13}Hello, good. Hi, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.54,0:51:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是萊克斯 幸會\N{\fs13}Lex. It is a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.49,0:51:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,手勁真大\N{\fs13}That is a good grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.41,0:51:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可別和這個人幹架\N{\fs13}You should not pick a fight with this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.46,0:51:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多年之後 我們終於把你請到大都會來了\N{\fs13}So, after all these years, we've finally got you over to Metropolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.25,0:51:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我來是想喝光你的酒 - 千萬別客氣\N{\fs13}- Well, I thought I'd come drink you dry. - Well, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.67,0:51:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你該常來港灣 我想帶你看看我的實驗室\N{\fs13}You should hop the harbor more often, though.I'd love to show you my labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.09,0:51:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,或許我們可以在某方面合作\N{\fs13}Maybe we could partner on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.64,0:51:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的研發部喜歡各種邪門歪道\N{\fs13}My R&D is up to all sorts of no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.57,0:51:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,7分鐘了\N{\fs13}That's 7 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.72,0:51:44.89,TOP,,0,0,0,,傳輸完成
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.18,0:51:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看來傳輸完成了\N{\fs13}Look likes the transfer's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.51,0:51:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 盧瑟先生 - 什麼事\N{\fs13}- Mr. Luthor. -  Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.78,0:51:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是州長 - 州長\N{\fs13}- The governor. - Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.70,0:51:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 失陪了 - 下次聊\N{\fs13}- Excuse me. - Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.04,0:51:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 州長 嗨 - 萊克斯 很高興見到你\N{\fs13}- Governor, hi. - Lex, it's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.30,0:52:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一場致命的工廠大火打斷了華雷斯的亡靈節慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.83,0:52:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾下\N{\fs13}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.58,0:52:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信 他們任由那可憐的女孩死去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.76,0:53:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們 作為這個星球上的一個族群 一直在尋找一個救世主\N{\fs13}We, as a population on this planet, have been looking for a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.84,0:53:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,90％的人都信仰神力\N{\fs13}90% of people believe in a higher power.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.43,0:53:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,每一個宗教都信奉著某種救世主形象\N{\fs13}And every religion believes in some sort messianic figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.68,0:53:53.47,TOP,,0,0,0,,維克拉姆·甘地 紀錄片導演\N超人問題
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.77,0:53:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,當這個救世主角色真的來到地球時\N{\fs13}And when this savior character actually comes to Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.79,0:53:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要讓他遵守我們的規則?\N{\fs13}we want to make him abide by our rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.15,0:53:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須明白 這是一個範式轉變\N{\fs13}We have to understand that this is a paradigm shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.48,0:54:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須開始思考超越政治的東西\N{\fs13}We have to start thinking beyond politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.86,0:54:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人身上有任何道德約束嗎\N{\fs13}Are there any moral constraints on this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.61,0:54:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有國際法\N{\fs13}We have international law.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.38,0:54:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個地球上 每一個行為都是一種政治行為\N{\fs13}On this Earth, every act is a political act.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.57,0:54:07.93,TOP,,0,0,0,,安德魯·蘇利文 [ 暢銷書作家 ]\N超人的行為具有政治性
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.91,0:54:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最強大的人是一個有爭議的人物\N{\fs13}Is it really surprising, that the most powerful man in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.88,0:54:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這真的令人驚訝嗎\N{\fs13}should be a figure of controversy?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.00,0:54:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,讓一個個體參與國家事務\N{\fs13}To have an individual engaging in the state level interventions
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.33,0:54:18.42,TOP,,0,0,0,,瓊·芬奇議員\N肯塔基州(民主黨)
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.92,0:54:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這應該讓我們深思\N{\fs13}should give us all pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.30,0:54:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,人類有一段可怕的過去 追隨強權人物\N{\fs13}Human beings have a horrible track record of following people with great power
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.60,0:54:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,並導致了嚴重的人類暴行\N{\fs13}down paths that led to huge human atrocities.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.76,0:54:29.26,TOP,,0,0,0,,格倫·伍德伯恩\N海外博主
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.14,0:54:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直在以我們自己的形象創造崇拜對像\N{\fs13}We have always created icons in our own image.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.89,0:54:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們所做的就是把我們自己投射到他身上\N{\fs13}What we've done is we project ourselves on to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.23,0:54:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,事實是 也許他不是某種魔鬼或耶穌的角色\N{\fs13}The fact is, maybe he's not some sort of devil or Jesus character.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.06,0:54:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也許他只是一個試圖做正確之事的人\N{\fs13}Maybe he's just a guy trying to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.53,0:54:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在談論的是一個真實存在的生命體\N{\fs13}We're talking about a being whose very existence
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.65,0:54:50.41,TOP,,0,0,0,,尼爾·德哥拉斯·泰森\N天體物理學家 宇宙論者 作家
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.73,0:54:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,挑戰了我們自身在宇宙中對優先級的認識\N{\fs13}challenges our own sense of priority in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.19,0:54:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你追溯哥白尼 那時他重建了\N{\fs13}If you go back to Copernicus, where he restored
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.69,0:54:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,已知的宇宙中心 用太陽取代了地球\N{\fs13}the sun in the center of the known universe, displacing earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.12,0:54:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再看看達爾文的進化論\N{\fs13}And you get to Darwinian evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.29,0:55:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就會發現 我們在地球上不是特殊的\N{\fs13}and you find out, we're not special on this Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.38,0:55:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只是其他生命形式中的一種\N{\fs13}we're just one among other life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.01,0:55:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我們瞭解到 我們甚至在整個宇宙中都不是特殊的\N{\fs13}And now we learned, that we're not even special in the entire universe
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.80,0:55:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有超人\N{\fs13}because there is Superman.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.17,0:55:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在那裏 一個在我們之中的外星人\N{\fs13}There he is. An alien among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.88,0:55:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們並不孤單\N{\fs13}We're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.92,0:55:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,作為一名美國議員 你是說你能自在地\N{\fs13}Are you, as a United State Senator, personally comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.43,0:55:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,親自向一對悲傷的父母說 超人原本可以救你們的孩子\N{\fs13}saying to a grieving parent, "Superman could've saved your child,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.26,0:55:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但原則上 我們不希望他採取行動?\N{\fs13}but on principle we did not want him to act."?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.70,0:55:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說他不該採取行動\N{\fs13}I'm not saying he shouldn't act.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.28,0:55:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說他不該單方面採取行動\N{\fs13}I'm saying he shouldn't act unilaterally.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.54,0:55:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們在這裏討論的是什麼呢\N{\fs13}What are we talking about here then?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.79,0:55:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是否必須要有一個超人?\N{\fs13}Must there be a Superman?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.35,0:55:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,已經有了\N{\fs13}There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.83,0:55:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs13}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.80,0:55:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,媽\N{\fs13}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.87,0:55:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\N{\fs13}Clark.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.60,0:56:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事 怎麼了\N{\fs13}What is it?What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.93,0:56:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 我只是...\N{\fs13}No,nothing.I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.03,0:56:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs13}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.33,0:56:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs13}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.00,0:56:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸怎麼從沒離開過堪薩斯\N{\fs13}How come Dad never left Kansas?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.78,0:56:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是...\N{\fs13}Well, he just...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.51,0:56:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他是什麼樣的人\N{\fs13}You know how he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.36,0:56:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而我要旅行幹嘛呢 我已經旅行了\N{\fs13}What do I need to travel for? I'm already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.20,0:56:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望事情能更簡單些\N{\fs13}I just wished it was more simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.62,0:56:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的寶貝孩子\N{\fs13}My baby boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.86,0:56:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼事是簡單的\N{\fs13}Nothing was ever simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.86,0:56:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一個奇怪的小東西\N{\fs13}An odd little duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.07,0:56:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我從沒見過這樣的金屬\N{\fs13}I've never seen a metal like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.70,0:57:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是國防部高級研究計劃局的黑匣子\N{\fs13}Could be darpa black box.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.54,0:57:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,誰能搞清楚呢\N{\fs13}Well, who could find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.08,0:57:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人想搞清楚\N{\fs13}Nobody who'd want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.96,0:57:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,或許他們把這些給反叛軍是為了做戰地測試\N{\fs13}Maybe they gave them out to the rebels to test in theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.88,0:57:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把活人士兵當實驗動物用?\N{\fs13}Using live soldiers as guinea pigs?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.05,0:57:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以是個如此出色的記者\N{\fs13}And this is what makes you such a good reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.57,0:57:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為這種事還是會使你震驚\N{\fs13}Stuff like this still shocks you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.10,0:57:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哥譚自由報
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.43,0:57:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對哥譚市的犯人們來說 蝙蝠烙印就是死刑判決
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.44,0:57:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,星球日報  幾十個罪犯被標上了蝙蝠烙印\N被烙者在哥譚臭名昭著的黑門監獄有安全風險
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.28,0:57:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠俠在充當法官 陪審團及處刑人\N哥譚身著披風的犯罪鬥士是不是太過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.08,0:57:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,弄不掉了 弄不掉了\N{\fs13}It don't come off!It don't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.05,0:57:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,移交囚犯\N{\fs13}Prisoner transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.33,0:57:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能把我關進普通牢房 老兄 他們會殺了我\N{\fs13}You can't put me in general, man.  They gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.63,0:57:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你不能帶我去普通牢房\N{\fs13}Hey, you can't bring me to general.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.00,0:57:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該感謝大都會的納稅人們\N{\fs13}You should be thanking the tax payers of Metropolis
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.80,0:57:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,收容你這被烙的混蛋\N{\fs13}for taking in your branded ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.63,0:57:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 請簽字 - 我被標記了 老兄\N{\fs13}- Sign in please. - I'm marked, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.88,0:57:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他們對有這東西的人會做什麼嗎\N{\fs13}You know what they do to people with this on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.13,0:57:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是個罪犯\N{\fs13}He's only a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.19,0:57:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這邊 快走 他們會殺了我\N{\fs13} - This way! Let's go! - They're gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.69,0:57:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他們會殺了我 - 快走\N{\fs13}- They're gonna kill me! - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.51,0:58:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,基夫 你被保釋了 打開二號\N{\fs13}Keefe, you made bail. Open Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.81,0:58:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,誰出的錢\N{\fs13}Who paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.16,0:58:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰\N{\fs13}Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.03,0:58:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就是個人而已 - 是嗎\N{\fs13}- Just a man. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.81,0:58:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你他媽想幹嘛\N{\fs13}What the fuck you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.50,0:58:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,幫你坐穩立場\N{\fs13}To help you stand for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.23,0:58:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你三點的預約到了\N{\fs13}Your 3 o'clock's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.69,0:58:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他讓我成了一個不完整的男人\N{\fs13}He made me half a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.97,0:58:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子\N{\fs13}My wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.08,0:59:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,離開了我\N{\fs13}...walked out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.07,0:59:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至不能站著小便\N{\fs13}I can't even piss standing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.46,0:59:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我對質他\N{\fs13}Let me face him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.00,0:59:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你會處理好吧?\N{\fs13}You'll take care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.22,0:59:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs13}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.08,0:59:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.09,0:59:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,退後 讓開\N{\fs13}Back up! Make a hole!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.57,1:00:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,走錯地方了 小姐\N{\fs13}Wrong room, miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.64,1:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萬維克部長 你一直沒回我電話\N{\fs13}Secretary Swanwick, you haven't been returning my phone calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.34,1:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,萊恩小姐 如果你想採訪 那扇門外面就能找到法裏斯少校\N{\fs13}Miss Lane, if you like an interview, Major Farris is just outside that door.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.13,1:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我當成陌生人?\N{\fs13}You're treating me like a stranger?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.55,1:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你當成記者\N{\fs13}I'm treating you like a reporter.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.63,1:00:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs13}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.80,1:00:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,美國在向非洲的反叛軍提供實驗性軍用武器嗎\N{\fs13}Is the US providing experimental military arms to rebels in Africa?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.10,1:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼有膽量的人\N{\fs13}You know with balls like yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.61,1:00:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,應該屬於這裏\N{\fs13}You belong in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.75,1:00:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的消息來源是什麼 錫箔帽嗎\N{\fs13}What's your source on this? A tin foil hat?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.84,1:00:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是錫 是金屬\N{\fs13}No, not tin, but it's metal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.17,1:00:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在那次超人事件中射出的 五角大樓的專家都無法識別它\N{\fs13}Fired in the Superman incident. Experts at the Pentagon can't ID it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.93,1:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我們沒有被告知真相 - 真相就是\N{\fs13}- We haven't been told the truth. - Here's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.53,1:00:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一名記者貪求獨家新聞 去了她不該去的地方\N{\fs13}A reporter got greedy for a scoop and went where she shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.41,1:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,超人救她時 就像兵痞似的 還導致了多人死亡\N{\fs13}Superman acted like some... rogue combatant to rescue her and people died.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.29,1:00:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要編造陰謀論來放回他的聖環\N{\fs13}Don't invent a conspiracy theory to put back his halo.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.35,1:00:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,或你的聖環\N{\fs13}Or yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.69,1:00:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 少校 - 長官\N{\fs13}- Major. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.57,1:01:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我登錄了你的網盤找復件\N{\fs13}So, I logged into your drop box to find a copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.57,1:01:03.53,TOP,,0,0,0,,體育版\N弱旅夢碎 哥譚與榮耀 相隔10碼
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.45,1:01:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了這個復件\N{\fs13}There's a copy, alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.66,1:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但卻沒有關於橄欖球的 沒有關於...\N{\fs13}But, nothing about football. Nothing about...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.23,1:01:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會圖書館的那些朋友的 只有...\N{\fs13}Friends of the Metropolis Library, just...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.92,1:01:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的哥譚蝙蝠的事 我跟你說了別追\N{\fs13}The god damn Gotham bat thing, I told you not to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.71,1:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,警方不會幫忙 媒體不得不做正確的事\N{\fs13}The police won't help, the press has to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.03,1:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,輪不到你來決定是什麼正確的\N{\fs13}You don't get to decide what the right thing is.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.67,1:01:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,星球報社成立時 是有立場的 佩裏\N{\fs13}When the Planet was founded, it stood for something, Perry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.13,1:01:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,1938年時 的確如此 但現在不是1938年\N{\fs13}So could you, if it was 1938, but it's not 1938.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.04,1:01:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,公共事業振興署不再僱人了 一堆蘋果也不再只值幾分錢\N{\fs13}WPA aren't hiring no more. Apples don't cost a nickel.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.40,1:01:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏不准追 外面也不准 放掉這件事\N{\fs13}Not in here. Not out there. You drop this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.66,1:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人在意克拉克·肯特叫板蝙蝠俠\N{\fs13}Nobody cares about Clark Kent taking on the Batman.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.98,1:01:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以很顯然 超人\N{\fs13}So apparently superman
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.78,1:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不再希望我們把他當成美國人\N{\fs13}doesn't want us to think of him as American anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.15,1:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,說真的 我們何必呢\N{\fs13}And really, why would we?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.12,1:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是除了那身紅藍服裝 還有...\N{\fs13}I mean aside from the red and blue costume. And...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.17,1:01:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 美利堅合眾國的\N{\fs13}I don't know, the fact that he has
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.62,1:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,英文縮寫 有三分之一都在他的胸口上了\N{\fs13}one-third of the usa's initials on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.79,1:01:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜他沒有把獨立宣言\N{\fs13}I assume the only reason he's not wearing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.39,1:01:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,當披風來穿的唯一原因就是...\N{\fs13}the declaration of independence as a cape is...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.36,1:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他覺得這樣做太招搖了\N{\fs13}He thinks it's too on- the- nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.70,1:01:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這裏在搞什麼 - 不好\N{\fs13}- What is going on back here? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.43,1:02:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,夥計們 快點 走了\N{\fs13}Guys, come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.70,1:02:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神 快出去\N{\fs13}Get yourselves together and get out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.67,1:02:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把那些玻璃杯都放托盤上\N{\fs13}Get those glasses on those trays.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.80,1:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有客人口渴著呢\N{\fs13}We got thirsty people out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.27,1:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,半滿 記住 半滿\N{\fs13}Half full. Remember, half full.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.11,1:02:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能失陪一下嗎\N{\fs13}I wonder, would you excuse us?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.60,1:02:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想帶你看樣東西 - 抱歉\N{\fs13}- There's something I'd like to show you. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.75,1:02:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,現在有些學者堅持認為那件事從沒發生過...\N{\fs13}Now some scholars insist that it never happened...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.05,1:02:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但我相信那種行為\N{\fs13}But I believe it's the action
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.06,1:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,完全符合一個既是國王又是變態殺手的人\N{\fs13}perfectly in keeping with a king who was also a psychopathic killer.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.93,1:02:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對我而言 這是40年策展的巔峰\N{\fs13}For me, it's the culmination of 40 years curating.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.70,1:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我簡直不敢相信 我終於把它弄來了\N{\fs13}And I can't believe it, but I've finally got it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.97,1:02:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,它就是亞歷山大之劍\N{\fs13}It's the sword of Alexander.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.44,1:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,砍斷戈爾迪之結的那把劍\N{\fs13}It's the blade that cut the gordian knot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.88,1:02:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一場勝利\N{\fs13}It's a triumph.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.25,1:02:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,的確\N{\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.71,1:02:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好好欣賞吧 - 謝謝\N{\fs13}- Enjoy. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.79,1:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一件贗品\N{\fs13}It's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.49,1:03:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真品在98年時在黑市上被賣了\N{\fs13}The real one was sold in '98 on the black market.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.29,1:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,現在它掛在...\N{\fs13}And now it hangs...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.46,1:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,掛在哈傑爾蘇丹的床上方\N{\fs13}Over the bed of the sultan of hajar.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.07,1:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪了\N{\fs13}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.64,1:03:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 小姐\N{\fs13}Excuse me, miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.74,1:03:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,前幾天晚上 你拿了不屬於你的東西\N{\fs13}The other night you took something that doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.97,1:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,偷是沒教養的\N{\fs13}Stealing's not polite.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.14,1:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果從另一個小偷那兒偷 也算偷嗎\N{\fs13}Is it stealing if you steal from another thief?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.65,1:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什麼人\N{\fs13}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.28,1:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,某個和你關注同一個人的人\N{\fs13}Someone interested in the same man you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.18,1:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎\N{\fs13}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.79,1:03:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信盧瑟先生有一張屬於我的照片\N{\fs13}I believe Mr. Luthor has a photograph that belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.86,1:03:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿到了嗎\N{\fs13}Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.56,1:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,事實上 沒 我沒拿到\N{\fs13}As it happens, no, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.86,1:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你複製的數據都有軍工級加密\N{\fs13}The data you copied has military- grade encryption.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.30,1:03:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我用你這身禮服打賭\N{\fs13}You know, i bet with that dress,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.69,1:03:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,十個男人裏有九個願意讓你順走任何東西\N{\fs13}9 out of 10 men will let you get away with anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.47,1:03:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是那第十個?\N{\fs13}But you're the 10th?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.97,1:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我是第一個\N{\fs13}I'm guessing I'm the first
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.38,1:03:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看穿你那低幼把戲的男人\N{\fs13}to see through that babe-in-the-woods act.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.81,1:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不瞭解我\N{\fs13}You don't know me,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.48,1:03:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但我認識幾個你這樣的女人\N{\fs13}but I've known a few women like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.62,1:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不覺得你見過我這樣的女人\N{\fs13}Oh, I don't think you've ever known a woman like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.22,1:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,人們對於小男孩的說法一點沒錯\N{\fs13}You know, it's true what they say about little boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.33,1:04:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,天生不會分享\N{\fs13}Born with no natural inclination to share.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.30,1:04:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒偷你的硬盤\N{\fs13}I didn't steal your drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.53,1:04:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是借用\N{\fs13}I borrowed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.80,1:04:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你會在你車上的儲物箱裏找到它的\N{\fs13}You'll find it in the glove compartment of your car.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.01,1:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再見 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}Mr. Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.44,1:04:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,已連接
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.78,1:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,已連接
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.66,1:04:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,開始解密
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.87,1:04:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,密解中
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.83,1:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,密解中
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.35,1:06:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你們拿到了嗎\N{\fs13}Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.49,1:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那塊石頭\N{\fs13}The rock?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.82,1:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們拿到了\N{\fs13}Yeah, we got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.53,1:06:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.95,1:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs13}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.72,1:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蹲下 快蹲下\N{\fs13}Get down! Get down now!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.90,1:07:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.82,1:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的世界\N{\fs13}She was my world.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.16,1:09:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而你把她從我這奪走了\N{\fs13}And you took her from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.86,1:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯斯\N{\fs13}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.07,1:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯斯 現在聽我說\N{\fs13}Bruce! Listen to me now!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.12,1:09:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是露易絲\N{\fs13}It's Lois!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.16,1:09:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是露易絲·萊恩\N{\fs13}It's Lois Lane!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.65,1:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她是關鍵\N{\fs13}She's the key!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.02,1:09:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我來太早了嗎\N{\fs13}Am I too soon?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.02,1:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我來太早了\N{\fs13}I'm too soon!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.53,1:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你對他的看法沒錯\N{\fs13}You're right about him!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.86,1:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你對他的看法一直是對的\N{\fs13}You've always been right about him!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.89,1:09:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,警惕他 警惕他\N{\fs13}Fear him! Fear him!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.87,1:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,找到我們 布魯斯\N{\fs13}Find us, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.04,1:09:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你必須找到我們\N{\fs13}You have to find us!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.70,1:10:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,解密完成\N正在加載萊克斯操作系統
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.99,1:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.30,1:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哥譚自由報\N蝙蝠烙印下的正義
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.30,1:10:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,人販被烙上\N蝙蝠俠的標記
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.63,1:10:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.84,1:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,白葡萄牙人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.02,1:10:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,法官
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.14,1:10:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,陪審團
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.65,1:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,處刑人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.78,1:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,正義?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.70,1:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,白葡萄牙人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.93,1:11:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,白葡萄牙人不是一個人\N{\fs13}The white Portuguese is not a man.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.59,1:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而是一艘船\N{\fs13}It's a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.01,1:11:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩老爺 你從七歲起\N{\fs13}Master Wayne, since the age of seven
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.18,1:11:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,對騙術的掌握就好比\N{\fs13}you have been to the art of deception
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.26,1:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,莫扎特之於大鍵琴一般高超\N{\fs13}as Mozart to the harpsichord.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.72,1:11:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但你從來都不善於對我撒謊\N{\fs13}But you've never been too hot at lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.42,1:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,白葡萄牙人裝載的不是髒彈\N{\fs13}The white Portuguese is not carrying a dirty bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.61,1:11:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,裝載的是什麼\N{\fs13}What is it carrying?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.26,1:11:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一件武器\N{\fs13}It's a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.40,1:11:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是一塊石頭\N{\fs13}It's a rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.13,1:11:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一種能讓氪星人細胞衰弱的礦物\N{\fs13}A mineral capable of weakening Kryptonian cells.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.73,1:11:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,三個月前 第一塊足夠大到有用的樣本\N{\fs13}The first sample big enough to mean something
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.66,1:11:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,出現在了印度洋中\N{\fs13}turned up in the Indian ocean three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.62,1:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,它現在在白葡萄牙人上\N{\fs13}It is now aboard the white Portuguese
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.67,1:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,被送到萊克斯·盧瑟那裏\N{\fs13}being delivered to Lex Luthor.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.13,1:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而我要從他那裏偷走它\N{\fs13}Who I am going to steal it from.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.01,1:11:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不讓它落到盧瑟手裏\N{\fs13}To keep it out of Luthor's hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.95,1:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,為了摧毀它\N{\fs13}To destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.65,1:11:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.49,1:11:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要開戰?\N{\fs13}You're gonna go to war?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.92,1:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那個混蛋兩年前就給我們帶來了戰爭\N{\fs13}That son of a bitch brought the war to us two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.93,1:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶 阿爾弗雷德 數數死亡人數吧 有上千人啊\N{\fs13}Jesus, Alfred. Count the dead. Thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.80,1:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來呢 上百萬嗎\N{\fs13}What's next? Millions?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.64,1:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他擁有抹去整個人類的力量\N{\fs13}He has the power to wipe out the entire human race,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.49,1:12:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕我們認為他只有1%的可能是我們的敵人\N{\fs13}and if we believe there's even a 1% chance that he is our enemy,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.24,1:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都必須把這可能性當成絕對的\N{\fs13}we have to take it as an absolute certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.28,1:12:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須消滅他\N{\fs13}And we have to destroy him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.78,1:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不是我們的敵人\N{\fs13}But he is not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.20,1:12:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不是\N{\fs13}Not today.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.41,1:12:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾弗雷德 哥譚這20年間\N{\fs13}20 years in Gotham, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.69,1:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都見識了承諾的份量\N{\fs13}We've seen what promises are worth.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.82,1:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,還剩多少善良的人\N{\fs13}How many good guys are left.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.86,1:12:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又有多少人一直如此\N{\fs13}How many stayed that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.72,1:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,給你14個小時\N{\fs13}14 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.89,1:12:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫克拉克·肯特 來自星球日報\N{\fs13}My name is Clark Kent. I'm from the daily planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.02,1:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想瞭解一個叫桑托斯的囚犯發生了什麼事\N{\fs13}I'm trying to find out what happened to an inmate, a Santos.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.31,1:12:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能對外公佈這個信息\N{\fs13}I can't give out that information.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.50,1:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠來了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.23,1:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.50,1:13:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,桑托斯夫人\N{\fs13}Mrs. Santos?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.91,1:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我能問你幾個問題嗎\N{\fs13}May I ask you a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.38,1:13:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是我的丈夫\N{\fs13}He wasn't my husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.18,1:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道他幹了什麼\N{\fs13}But I know what he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.06,1:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是一個父親\N{\fs13}But he was a father.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.88,1:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他也身為人父\N{\fs13}He was that, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.85,1:13:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把他帶離哥譚中央警署\N{\fs13}They took him out of Gotham central.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.61,1:13:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,把他轉移到了大都會\N{\fs13}They moved him to Metropolis.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.69,1:13:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們心裏清楚\N{\fs13}But inside they know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.59,1:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他們完全清楚那個標記 可警衛不管\N{\fs13}They know the mark all over. Guards don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.09,1:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠就是法官\N{\fs13}Bat's the judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.56,1:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一個決定誰生誰死的人\N{\fs13}One man decides who lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.26,1:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那樣的正義算什麼 - 跟我說說\N{\fs13}- How is that justice? - Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.77,1:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 幫我來改變它 - 用什麼 你的筆嗎\N{\fs13}- Help me change it. - With what? Your pen?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.00,1:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他那種人 沒法用文字阻止\N{\fs13}A man like that, words don't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.74,1:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道什麼能阻止他嗎\N{\fs13}You know what stops him?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.87,1:13:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拳頭\N{\fs13}A fist.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.47,1:13:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,肯特 我要和你談談\N{\fs13}Kent, I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.67,1:13:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,星球日報
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.92,1:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,肯特\N{\fs13}Kent!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.45,1:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他去哪了 珍妮 他去哪了\N{\fs13}Where does he go? Where does he go, Jenny?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.77,1:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不...我不知道\N{\fs13}I don't... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.62,1:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋跟互碰了三次\N{\fs13}Clicks his heels three times,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.62,1:14:07.52,TOP,,0,0,0,,注:改自小說《綠野僊蹤》中的句子\N原是桃樂絲將其鞋跟互碰三下就能回老家
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.07,1:14:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,回堪薩斯去了吧\N{\fs13}goes back to Kansas, i suppose.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.43,1:14:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,混...\N{\fs13}Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.61,1:14:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,白葡萄牙人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.08,1:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,放\N{\fs13}Turn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.84,1:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放\N{\fs13}Turn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.93,1:15:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.82,1:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,收隊\N{\fs13}Move out!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.08,1:15:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克爾森集散站及碼頭公司
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.46,1:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快開 快開 快開 快開\N{\fs13}Go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.63,1:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,鏢槍
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.58,1:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.88,1:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fs13}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.76,1:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他們下次再用你的燈照耀天空\N{\fs13}Next time they shine your light in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.75,1:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,別去了\N{\fs13}don't go to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.30,1:19:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠已經死了 埋了它吧\N{\fs13}The bat is dead. Bury it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.30,1:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就當是我手下留情\N{\fs13}Consider this mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.05,1:19:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我\N{\fs13}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.61,1:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你會流血嗎\N{\fs13}Do you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.94,1:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你會的\N{\fs13}You will.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.35,1:20:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,搜索應答器信號
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.29,1:20:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,追蹤完成 已找到應答器方位\N萊克斯集團研究園
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.39,1:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我頭上可沒聖環 部長先生\N{\fs13}I don't have a halo over me, Mr. secretary.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.51,1:21:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了沙漠 那裏有人死了\N{\fs13}I went into the desert, people died.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.38,1:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這讓我難以入睡 這是當然的\N{\fs13}It keeps me awake. It should.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.21,1:21:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你認為超人是兇手\N{\fs13}If you think that superman is a murderer,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.91,1:21:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那就把它扔了吧\N{\fs13}then throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.91,1:21:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但我相信你不那麼認為\N{\fs13}But I don't believe you think that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.88,1:21:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們如何確定什麼是善意呢\N{\fs13}How do we determine what's good?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.92,1:21:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在民主國家 善意就是溝通交流\N{\fs13}In a democracy, good is a conversation,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.91,1:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而非單方面的決定\N{\fs13}not a unilateral decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.63,1:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我敦促超人\N{\fs13}So I urge superman to come
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.30,1:22:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,明天到這座人民之山來\N{\fs13}to this hill of the people tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.10,1:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看看那些遭受了痛苦的人\N{\fs13}to see those who have suffered.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.30,1:22:02.50,TOP,,0,0,0,,芬奇議員新聞發佈會
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.80,1:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,世界需要知道在那片沙漠中發生了什麼\N{\fs13}The world needs to know what happened in that desert.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.87,1:22:07.59,TOP,,0,0,0,,芬奇議員新聞發佈會
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.07,1:22:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,需要知道他的立場\N{\fs13}And to know what he stands for.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.57,1:22:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他會將他的力量用到哪種程度\N{\fs13}How far will he take his power?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.31,1:22:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他是根據我們的意志行事 還是根據他自己的意志\N{\fs13}Does he act by our will or by his own?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.95,1:22:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,人們討厭他們不理解的東西\N{\fs13}People hate what they don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.46,1:22:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們看見你的所作所為 就會瞭解你\N{\fs13}But they see what you do, and they know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.63,1:22:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是殺手 也不是威脅\N{\fs13}You're not a killer, a threat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.40,1:22:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來都不希望這個世界擁有你\N{\fs13}I never wanted this world to have you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.14,1:22:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,做他們的英雄 克拉克 做他們的豐碑\N{\fs13}Be their hero, Clark. Be their monument.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.67,1:22:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,做他們的天使\N{\fs13}Be their angel.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.51,1:22:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,做他們需要你做的\N{\fs13}Be anything they need you to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.68,1:22:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,或者什麼都不做\N{\fs13}Or be none of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.78,1:22:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不欠這世界任何東西\N{\fs13}You don't owe this world a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.99,1:23:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,從來都不欠\N{\fs13}You never did.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.69,1:23:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,德尼羅斯到了 可換乘至凱恩大道\N{\fs13}This is deniros. Transfer available to Kane Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.52,1:23:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,請當心腳下\N{\fs13}Please, mind your step.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.18,1:23:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我必須跟議員談話\N{\fs13}I have to speak to the senator today.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.13,1:23:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你不能見議員\N{\fs13}You cannot see the senator today.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.77,1:23:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要在聽證會之前跟她談話\N{\fs13}I need to speak to her before the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.39,1:23:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白這有多重要嗎\N{\fs13}Do you understand how important this is?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.23,1:23:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能讓你見議員\N{\fs13}I cannot let you see the senator.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.27,1:23:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 我得跟她說話\N{\fs13}Please, I need to speak to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.47,1:23:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 女士 我求你了 請別這樣\N{\fs13}Please, madam. I beg of you! Please don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.37,1:23:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這十分重要\N{\fs13}This is so important!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.88,1:23:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟我來 - 別碰我\N{\fs13}- Come with me. - Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.41,1:23:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 求你了 - 對不起 她不肯走\N{\fs13}- Please! - I'm sorry. She wouldn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.38,1:24:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒告訴你真相\N{\fs13}I didn't tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.19,1:24:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,中情局認為沙漠那件事是個圈套\N{\fs13}C.I.A Thinks the desert was a setup.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.09,1:24:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有人想加罪於超人\N{\fs13}Somebody wanted superman to look guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.50,1:24:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那子彈呢\N{\fs13}The bullet?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.30,1:24:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那種金屬是一家私人公司開發的\N{\fs13}The metal was developed by a private company.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.47,1:24:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼公司\N{\fs13}What company?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.35,1:24:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團\N{\fs13}Lexcorp.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.14,1:24:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯·盧瑟?\N{\fs13}Lex Luthor?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.39,1:24:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他還在那個沙漠圍場安插了他的私人僱傭兵\N{\fs13}He also had private security contractors at the desert compound.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.55,1:24:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,公開出來\N{\fs13}Go on record.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.36,1:24:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不可能 這是機密\N{\fs13}Not a chance. It's classified.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.91,1:24:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我又恰好喜歡我的工作\N{\fs13}I happen to like my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.20,1:24:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這說不通\N{\fs13}It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.41,1:24:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你說那個圈套是為了陷害超人\N{\fs13}You said that the ambush was arranged to frame superman,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.49,1:24:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們怎麼會知道他會出現在...\N{\fs13}but how could they know that he'd show up in the...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.73,1:24:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那片沙漠中 謝謝\N{\fs13}In the middle of the desert. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.71,1:24:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 過來\N{\fs13}Alright, come on through.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.27,1:25:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,參議院聽證會現在隨時可能開始\N{\fs13}The senate hearing is expected to get underway any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.88,1:25:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 最大的未知數就是\N{\fs13}And of course the big unknown in all of this is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.11,1:25:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,超人會出現嗎\N{\fs13}will superman show up?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.64,1:25:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是他們真正所期盼的\N{\fs13}That is what they're really waiting to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.77,1:25:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,基夫先生 基夫先生\N{\fs13}Mr. keefe. Mr. keefe.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.02,1:25:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是索莉戴·奧伯萊恩 此刻欄目的\N{\fs13}Soledad o'brien, in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.60,1:25:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,問你個問題\N{\fs13}Quick question for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.95,1:25:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要和議員們見面了\N{\fs13}You're heading in to meet with the senators.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.44,1:25:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你會跟他們說什麼\N{\fs13}What will you tell them?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.12,1:25:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來告訴他們該醒醒了\N{\fs13}I've come here to tell them to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.06,1:25:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這是血和肉的事實\N{\fs13}This is flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.23,1:25:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經帶來了一場戰爭\N{\fs13}He has delivered a war here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.73,1:25:23.28,TOP,,0,0,0,,韋恩公司前僱員將出庭作證
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.86,1:25:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這個...\N{\fs13}And this...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.90,1:25:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是戰爭的樣貌\N{\fs13}This is what war looks like.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.74,1:25:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我一無所有了\N{\fs13}I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.79,1:25:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 有很多人會說他是他們的英雄\N{\fs13}There are plenty of people, sir, who would say he's their hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.80,1:25:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是英雄\N{\fs13}He is not a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.71,1:25:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾絲 能麻煩你讓格雷格上來嗎\N{\fs13}Grace, can you get Greg up here, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.48,1:25:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就現在\N{\fs13}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.68,1:25:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一個匿名線人能證明每一件\N{\fs13}An anonymous source can verify everything
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.88,1:25:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你所說在內羅米發生的事\N{\fs13}I told you about what happened in nairomi.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.05,1:25:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一個匿名線人? - 刊登出來\N{\fs13}- An anonymous source? Run it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.12,1:25:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,盧瑟策劃了沙漠事件\N{\fs13}Luthor engineered the desert.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.25,1:25:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那是給超人設的圈套\N{\fs13}It was an ambush for superman.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.42,1:25:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,相信你的記者 想想水門事件\N{\fs13}Trust your reporter. Think Watergate.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.10,1:25:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你得想想打官司的事\N{\fs13}Yeah, and you need to think litigate.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.13,1:25:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是錯的 盧瑟會把報社告到不復存在\N{\fs13}If you're wrong, Luthor will sue the paper out of existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.66,1:25:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要證據\N{\fs13}You need proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.83,1:25:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣 現在就得刊登出來\N{\fs13}No. It needs to run now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.73,1:25:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在聽證會之前\N{\fs13}Before the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.03,1:25:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果超人知道了 或許會改變他的說辭\N{\fs13}If superman knows, it might change what he says.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.69,1:25:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會拿報社冒險\N{\fs13}I am not going to risk the paper
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.80,1:26:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好讓你在課堂上給你的救命恩人遞紙條\N{\fs13}so that you can pass notes in class to the man that rescued you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.49,1:26:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他賄賂了她?\N{\fs13}He paid her?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.58,1:26:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是賄賂了她 他還威脅了她\N{\fs13}Not only paid her. He threatened her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.14,1:26:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,並給了她一份稿子熟記\N{\fs13}Gave her a script to learn.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.55,1:26:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她父母在家裏活得好好的\N{\fs13}Her parents are alive back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.32,1:26:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那姑娘良心發現了\N{\fs13}But the girl's got a conscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.32,1:26:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他一直在把委員會當他的木偶劇院來用 - 議員\N{\fs13}- He's been using the committee as his puppet theater. - Senator!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.95,1:26:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你好\N{\fs13}Hi, you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.80,1:26:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,別走開 我有話跟你說\N{\fs13}Don't go anywhere. I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.30,1:26:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,梅茜 你先進去\N{\fs13}Uh, you know what? Mercy, you go in
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.73,1:26:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我佔好座位\N{\fs13}and make sure no one takes my seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.89,1:26:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹嘛\N{\fs13}So what you been up to?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.16,1:26:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是來講講我的故事\N{\fs13}I'm just here to tell my story.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.39,1:26:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我想出資造一件威懾氪星人的武器\N{\fs13}That I was willing to finance a Kryptonian deterrent,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.64,1:26:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但一位肯塔基的資淺議員\N{\fs13}but a certain junior senator from Kentucky
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.73,1:26:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,決定要阻止\N{\fs13}decided to block it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.85,1:26:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 專議超人的委員會主席在安全問題上很手軟\N{\fs13}Yes, the chair of the committee on superman is soft on security.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.87,1:26:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 格雷格 為什麼他一直沒收到我們的支票 - 他收到了 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}- Greg, why hasn't he been getting our checks? - He is, Mr. Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.74,1:26:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他每個月都會收到一張受害人基金的支票\N{\fs13}He gets a check from the victims fund every month.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.21,1:26:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可他都退回了\N{\fs13}He returns them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.98,1:26:44.63,TOP,,0,0,0,,布魯斯·韋恩\N睜開你的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.71,1:26:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...在兩年前\N{\fs13}...who lost both his legs
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.07,1:26:46.32,TOP,,0,0,0,,我是你的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.53,1:26:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會的那些可怕事件中\N{\fs13}in those horrific events in Metropolis
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.87,1:26:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了他的雙腿\N{\fs13}that happened two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.32,1:26:49.70,TOP,,0,0,0,,韋恩無勝算
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.91,1:26:50.57,TOP,,0,0,0,,絕不休戰
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.58,1:26:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\fs13}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.91,1:26:51.70,TOP,,0,0,0,,我不會放過你
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.03,1:26:53.41,TOP,,0,0,0,,布魯斯·韋恩 = 瞎子
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.69,1:26:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我從沒看到過這些\N{\fs13}Why haven't I seen this?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.36,1:26:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我會查清楚的\N{\fs13}I'm sorry. I'll get to the bottom of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.39,1:27:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那 超人來了\N{\fs13}And there he is. Superman is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.25,1:27:01.13,TOP,,0,0,0,,參議院委員會聽證會
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.26,1:27:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的來到了美國國會大廈\N{\fs13}He is actually at the United States capitol.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.51,1:27:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這真的是一個歷史性時刻\N{\fs13}This is really a historic moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.68,1:27:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我們期望超人會\N{\fs13}Now we expect that superman will give
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.84,1:27:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,向議員 向美國人民\N{\fs13}some kind of a statement to the senate,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.91,1:27:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 還有向全世界 給出某種聲明\N{\fs13}to the American people, and, of course, to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.41,1:27:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他在這裏了 他來了\N{\fs13}He's here. He came.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.91,1:27:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他在國會大廈上面\N{\fs13}He's above the capitol. Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.41,1:27:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,待會的場面可不好應付啊 小瓊\N{\fs13}You are gonna be on the hot seat in there, junebug.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.23,1:27:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在農場長大的\N{\fs13}I grew up on a farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.75,1:27:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,豬我都鬥得過\N{\fs13}I know how to wrestle a pig.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.90,1:27:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道美國最古老的謊言嗎 議員\N{\fs13}Do you know the oldest lie in America, senator?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.46,1:27:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是 力量可以是無辜的\N{\fs13}It's that power can be innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.43,1:27:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好運\N{\fs13}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.56,1:28:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐...\N{\fs13}Oh, miss...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.73,1:28:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,魯迪 她能進去\N{\fs13}Rudy, she's good to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.86,1:28:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,超人=非法外星人 外星人不是美國人\N這裏是我們的世界 不是你的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.98,1:28:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,滾吧\N{\fs13}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.35,1:28:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 滾吧 快滾 - 超人 超人\N{\fs13}- Get out! Get out! - Superman! Superman!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.48,1:28:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,今早又收到一封 韋恩先生\N{\fs13}Another one came this morning, Mr. Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.26,1:29:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 我想感謝我們的證人\N{\fs13}Let me say at the outset that I'm grateful to our witness
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.23,1:29:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝他今天來到我們面前\N{\fs13}for coming before us today.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.07,1:29:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,民主就是這麼運作的\N{\fs13}This is how a democracy works.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.15,1:29:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們相互對話\N{\fs13}We talk to each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.90,1:29:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們根據民眾的意願行事 先生\N{\fs13}We act by the consent of the governed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.45,1:29:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾坐在這裏說過\N{\fs13}I have sat here before to say
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.53,1:29:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,委員會是不會容忍暗箱操作的\N{\fs13} that shadow interventions will not be tolerated by this committee.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.25,1:29:40.95,TOP,,0,0,0,,萊克斯·盧瑟先生\N萊克斯集團首席執行官
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.75,1:29:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也不會容忍謊言\N{\fs13}Neither will lies.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.04,1:29:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為今天是真相大白之日\N{\fs13}Because today is a day for truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.09,1:29:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因為只有說出...\N{\fs13}Because only by speaking...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.44,1:30:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只有攜手合作 我們才能...\N{\fs13}Only by working together can we...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.65,1:30:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,才能...\N{\fs13}Can we...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.75,1:30:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們才能創造一個自由 以及...\N{\fs13}Can we create a free, and a...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.12,1:30:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶的蜜桃茶
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.05,1:30:38.93,TOP,,0,0,0,,萊克斯·盧瑟先生\N萊克斯集團首席執行官
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.15,1:30:55.24,TOP,,0,0,0,,超人來到美國國會大廈
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.49,1:30:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs13}Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.89,1:31:20.98,TOP,,0,0,0,,超人來到美國國會大廈
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.31,1:31:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,畫面回到國會大廈\N{\fs13}We're back at the nation's capitol,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.89,1:31:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,此處出了大事\N{\fs13}where something is happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.73,1:31:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你害死了你的家人
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.54,1:31:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下\N{\fs13}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.87,1:31:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下 警官\N{\fs13}Excuse me, officer.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.25,1:31:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是媒體人士 讓我進去 可以嗎\N{\fs13}Member of the press. Can you let me in, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.72,1:31:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢深呼吸\N{\fs13}Breathe slowly and deeply.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.85,1:31:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你會沒事的\N{\fs13}You're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.73,1:32:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 我需要點空間來工作\N{\fs13}Thank you. I'm gonna need a little room to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.65,1:32:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,女士 看來你的頭部受傷了\N{\fs13}Ma'am, it appears you've suffered a head injury.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.78,1:32:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,請看著我手電的光\N{\fs13}I'm gonna need you to follow my light with your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.87,1:33:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩老爺\N{\fs13}Master Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.47,1:33:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩先生\N{\fs13}Mr. Wayne!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.71,1:33:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...就在超人作證的參議院聽證會大廳裏\N{\fs13}...in the senate hearing room where superman was testifying.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.58,1:33:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一起發生在國會大廈的災難性事件\N{\fs13}This is a catastrophic situation at our nation's capitol.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.68,1:33:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還沒得到確切數字\N{\fs13}We don't have exact numbers yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.31,1:33:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我可以告訴大家 已有十幾個人\N{\fs13}but I can tell you that more than a dozen people
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.22,1:33:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在這場爆炸中死亡\N{\fs13}have died in this explosion.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.14,1:33:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,急救人員已抵達現場\N{\fs13}First responders are at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.33,1:33:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他們仍在救出受害者\N{\fs13}They are still bringing victims out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.02,1:33:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,最初 超人也在爆炸後幫忙救出受害者\N{\fs13}Now initially, superman was helping bring victims out after the blast
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.60,1:33:36.10,TOP,,0,0,0,,爆炸震徹國會大廈
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.78,1:33:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但他現在似乎消失了...\N{\fs13}but he seems to have disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.77,1:33:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...引起了疑問\N{\fs13}...raising questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.60,1:33:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,卡麗·伯明翰在國會大廈現場為你報道\N{\fs13}Carrie Birmingham, reporting live from the nation's capital.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.70,1:33:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,國會警方現在已確認爆炸是由\N{\fs13}Capitol police are now confirming that the blast was caused
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.17,1:33:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,聽證會大廳裏的一個爆炸裝置造成的\N{\fs13}by an explosive device inside the hearing room.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.79,1:33:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯集團
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.15,1:34:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我再放一遍\N{\fs13}Run that one more time for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.23,1:34:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能放大那個嗎 - 好了 長官\N{\fs13}- Can you enhance that? - There you go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.91,1:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,國會警方向有線電視新聞網確認了\N{\fs13}Capitol police are confirming to CNN
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.69,1:35:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,引爆炸彈的嫌疑犯是\N{\fs13}that the suspected bomber is
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.11,1:35:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沃萊士·維農·基夫 目前這些消息...\N{\fs13}Wallace Vernon keefe. Now these sources...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.28,1:35:02.74,TOP,,0,0,0,,國會大廈發生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.66,1:35:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 還是我 你能不能...\N{\fs13}Clark, it's me again. Can you...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.32,1:35:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...可能是把爆炸裝置藏在輪椅內\N{\fs13}...could have gotten the explosive device into the hearing
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.79,1:35:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,帶入聽證會的\N{\fs13}by concealing them inside his wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.08,1:35:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,至於超人 他當時在場\N{\fs13}As for superman, he was in the room,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.96,1:35:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但顯然沒能阻止他\N{\fs13}but obviously failed to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.75,1:35:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒看見 小露\N{\fs13}I didn't see it, lo.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.77,1:35:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我就站在那裏 卻沒有看見\N{\fs13}I was standing right there and I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.83,1:35:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 這件事有幕後主使\N{\fs13}Clark, there are people behind this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.71,1:35:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒看見 恐怕是因為我就沒看過\N{\fs13}I'm afraid I didn't see it because I wasn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.17,1:35:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以來\N{\fs13}All this time,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.31,1:35:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我都在按照我父親的看法活著\N{\fs13}I've been living my life the way my father saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.01,1:35:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為一個鬼魂糾正錯誤\N{\fs13}Righting wrongs for a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.48,1:35:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以為自己來到這裏是為了行善\N{\fs13}Thinking I'm here to do good.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.66,1:35:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,超人一直都不是真實的\N{\fs13}Superman was never real.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.66,1:35:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那只不過是一個堪薩斯農民的夢想\N{\fs13}Just the dream of a farmer from Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.36,1:35:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對有些人來說 那個農民的夢想就是一切\N{\fs13}That farmer's dream is all some people have.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.87,1:35:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是給了他們希望的一切\N{\fs13}It's all that gives them hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.01,1:36:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這是有意義的\N{\fs13}This means something.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.22,1:36:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的世界是有過\N{\fs13}It did on my world.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.15,1:36:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可我的世界已不復存在\N{\fs13}My world doesn't exist anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.23,1:37:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎\N{\fs13}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.07,1:37:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,分析顯示飛船在以37%的效能運轉\N{\fs13}Analysis reveals ship operating at 37% efficiency.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.64,1:37:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否要接管操作\N{\fs13}Would you like to assume command?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.31,1:37:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs13}Yes, I would.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.31,1:37:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要\N{\fs13}Yes, I would.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.45,1:37:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 開始吧\N{\fs13}Very well. Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.45,1:37:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,氪星的檔案庫包含了十萬個不同世界的知識\N{\fs13}The Kryptonian archive contains knowledge from 100,000 different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.66,1:37:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs13}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.13,1:37:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,教我吧\N{\fs13}Teach me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.50,1:39:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,_檔案
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.24,1:39:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,超_人類
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.56,1:39:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,攝像頭 01\N2015年6月22日 上午10:13 法國 巴黎
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.02,1:39:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,攝像頭 01\N2015年6月22日 上午10:13 法國巴黎 聖徒街
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.45,1:40:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,比利時 1918年11月
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.14,1:40:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷山大·盧瑟\N{\fs13}Alexander Luthor,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.65,1:40:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,已接受你的安全權限覆蓋\N{\fs13}your security override has been accepted.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.35,1:40:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,創生室已準備分析基因樣本\N{\fs13}Genesis chamber ready to analyze genetic sample.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.87,1:40:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正在確認當前基因物質\N{\fs13}Acknowledging presence of genetic material.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.76,1:40:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,正在分析\N{\fs13}Analyzing.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.83,1:40:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我已識別出基因主人身份為坎多城的佐德將軍\N{\fs13}I've identified the host as general Zod of Kandor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.51,1:41:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,正在確認當前外來基因物質\N{\fs13}Acknowledging presence of foreign genetic material.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.18,1:41:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正在分析\N{\fs13}Analyzing.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.39,1:41:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你飛得太靠近太陽了\N{\fs13}You flew too close to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.39,1:41:12.75,TOP,,0,0,0,,注:借用了希臘神話中伊卡洛斯的故事
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.02,1:41:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你現在\N{\fs13}Now look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.19,1:41:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,警告 此為禁止行為\N{\fs13}Advising. Action forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.63,1:41:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,氪星議會已頒布相應律法\N{\fs13}It has been decreed by the council of Krypton
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.70,1:41:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止任何人給如此面目可憎的\N{\fs13}that none will ever again give life to a deformity
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.20,1:41:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,畸形體重注生命\N{\fs13}so hateful to sight and memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.79,1:41:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是無名的褻瀆\N{\fs13}The desecration without name.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.07,1:41:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那氪星議會在哪呢\N{\fs13}And where is the council of Krypton?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.38,1:41:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,被毀了 先生\N{\fs13}Destroyed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.75,1:41:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那就繼續吧\N{\fs13}Then proceed.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.88,1:41:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 正在準備生物蛹並開始變形\N{\fs13}Very well. Preparing chrysalis and commencing metamorphosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.82,1:41:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們的疑問是\N{\fs13}"And so we are left to wonder
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.73,1:41:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果超人注意到了危險而什麼都沒做\N{\fs13}"if superman was aware of the threat and did nothing,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.03,1:41:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那他和此次國會大廈的慘劇有關係嗎\N{\fs13}"was he then complicit in the capitol tragedy?"
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.78,1:41:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,肯特還是沒來?\N{\fs13}Still no Kent?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.53,1:41:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他的消失引起了不少疑問\N{\fs13}"His disappearance raises questions."
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.99,1:41:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒來\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.82,1:42:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很多問題沒有得到解答\N{\fs13}There are still so many unanswered questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.94,1:42:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,其中最主要的就是超人是否參與了\N{\fs13}Chief among them, whether superman was involved
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.45,1:42:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,此次襲擊的謀劃\N{\fs13}in the planning of this attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.79,1:42:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一個有著無限力量的個體\N{\fs13}I mean, here's an individual who has unlimited power,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.99,1:42:09.66,TOP,,0,0,0,,超人是否參與其中了?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.41,1:42:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,卻沒去阻止離他只有幾英尺的引爆者\N{\fs13}yet did nothing to stop the bomber just a few feet away from him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.41,1:42:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這對調查員們來說 不合情理\N{\fs13}It just doesn't add up for investigators.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.08,1:42:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,燒死他 燒死他 燒死他\N{\fs13}Burn him, burn him, burn him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.58,1:42:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,燒死他 燒死他 燒死他\N{\fs13}Burn him, burn him, burn him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.48,1:42:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,給他20美元 他就當沒看見你\N{\fs13}For twenty American, he didn't see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.65,1:42:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一樣\N{\fs13}Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.28,1:42:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道這山上不去
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.11,1:42:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他是來送死的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.92,1:43:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,援引當前一名熟悉此案的聯調局官員\N{\fs13}Now one FBI official familiar with this case
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.34,1:43:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我的原話\N{\fs13}told me they found quote,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.30,1:43:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在基夫公寓裏中了個大獎 發現了炸彈製造材料\N{\fs13}"a jackpot of bomb-making materials inside keefe's apartment."
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.93,1:43:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他們現在需要查明的是\N{\fs13}What they need to determine now is
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.52,1:43:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他是否在謀劃與實行過程中得到了他人的協助\N{\fs13}whether he had any help in the planning and execution of the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.06,1:43:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他們尚未排除\N{\fs13}And they haven't ruled out the idea
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.31,1:43:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,超人是同謀的可能\N{\fs13}that superman was a co-conspirator.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.11,1:43:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 我的線人們告訴我 他們在此事的調查中收到了\N{\fs13}Now, my sources are telling me they are getting a barrage of anonymous and credible tips
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.99,1:43:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大量匿名而又可靠的線索\N{\fs13}with all roads in this investigation
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.11,1:43:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,全都指向了那位氪星來客\N{\fs13}leading to the Kryptonian visitor.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.85,1:44:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 露易絲 你該走了\N{\fs13}All right, Lois. You gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.97,1:44:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他並不知道自己會死\N{\fs13}He didn't know he was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.34,1:44:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他還買了不少食物\N{\fs13}He just bought groceries.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.30,1:44:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那個輪椅和沙漠的那顆子彈\N{\fs13}The wheelchair and the bullet from the desert
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.26,1:44:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,都由同種金屬製成\N{\fs13}were made from the same metal.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.95,1:44:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 沙漠 聽證會\N{\fs13}I know. The desert. The hearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.51,1:44:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,盧瑟想要超人所到之處都是死亡\N{\fs13}Everywhere superman goes, Luthor wants death.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.42,1:44:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 盧瑟費了這麼大勁\N{\fs13}But, Luthor goes through all of that trouble...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.69,1:44:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,把輪椅做成了一顆炸彈\N{\fs13}Creates a bomb out of a wheelchair,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.23,1:44:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,卻又加以改造來降低爆炸威力?\N{\fs13}and then alters it to reduce the blast?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.02,1:44:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思\N{\fs13}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.86,1:44:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,輪椅內部襯了鉛\N{\fs13}The inside of the chair was lined with lead.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.00,1:44:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒法阻止\N{\fs13}You couldn't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.33,1:44:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看不見\N{\fs13}You couldn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.41,1:45:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯吧\N{\fs13}Something, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.68,1:45:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們堪薩斯人住在平原\N{\fs13}We men of Kansas live on a pancake,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.65,1:45:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要來山上\N{\fs13}so we come to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.75,1:45:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裏俯瞰河漫灘\N{\fs13}All downhill from here, down to the floodplain.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.56,1:45:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,農場就像在世界的最底端\N{\fs13}Farm at the bottom of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.39,1:45:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得有一季的洪水很猛\N{\fs13}I remember one season the water came bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.43,1:45:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那時我還不到12歲\N{\fs13}I couldn't have been 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.36,1:45:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸拿出了鏟子 我們拚命挖了一夜\N{\fs13}Dad had out the shovels and we went at it all night.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.37,1:46:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一直到我暈了過去\N{\fs13}We worked till, i think, I fainted.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.54,1:46:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們成功阻擋了洪水\N{\fs13}But we managed to stop the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.65,1:46:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們拯救了農場\N{\fs13}We saved the farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.61,1:46:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你奶奶給我烤了個蛋糕 誇我是英雄\N{\fs13}Your grandma baked me a cake. Said I was a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.25,1:46:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那天晚些時候 我們發現\N{\fs13}Later that day we found out
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.25,1:46:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是擋住了洪水\N{\fs13}we blocked the water all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.42,1:46:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可我們把它送回了上游\N{\fs13}We sent it upstream.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.92,1:46:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,朗家的整個農場都被沖走了\N{\fs13}The whole lang farm washed away.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.46,1:46:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我在吃我的英雄蛋糕時 他們的馬被淹了\N{\fs13}While I ate my hero cake, their horses were drowning.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.30,1:46:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前常在夢中聽見它們的嚎哭\N{\fs13}I used to hear them wailing in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.47,1:46:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的噩夢有停止過嗎\N{\fs13}Did the nightmares ever stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.74,1:46:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有\N{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.11,1:46:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,當我遇到你的母親時\N{\fs13}When I met your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.05,1:46:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她讓我相信這世界上還有美好存在\N{\fs13}She gave me faith that there's good in this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.28,1:46:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是我的世界\N{\fs13}She was my world.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.29,1:46:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你 兒子\N{\fs13}I miss you, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.80,1:47:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想你 爸爸\N{\fs13}I miss you too, dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.65,1:47:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你贏不了的\N{\fs13}You know you can't win this.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.99,1:47:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這是自殺\N{\fs13}It's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.33,1:47:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在比我父親死時的年紀還大\N{\fs13}I'm older now than my father ever was.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.70,1:47:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,或許這對我是唯一有意義的事\N{\fs13}This may be the only thing i do that matters.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.50,1:47:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,打擊犯罪二十年 毫無意義嗎\N{\fs13}20 years of fighting criminals amounts to nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.44,1:47:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,犯罪就像野草 阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}Criminals are like weeds, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.18,1:47:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,除掉一個 又會在原地長出另一個\N{\fs13}Pull one up, another grows in its place.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.65,1:47:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這關乎世界的未來\N{\fs13}This is about the future of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.62,1:47:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的遺贈\N{\fs13}This is my legacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.49,1:48:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親曾讓我坐在這裏\N{\fs13}My father sat me down right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.86,1:48:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我韋恩家族是靠什麼興起的\N{\fs13}Told me what Wayne manor was built on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.02,1:48:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵路 房地產 還有石油\N{\fs13}Railroads, real estates, and oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.53,1:48:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,第一代和法國人做生意大賺了一筆\N{\fs13}The first generation made their fortune trading with the French.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.20,1:48:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,毛皮生意\N{\fs13}Pelts and skins.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.70,1:48:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都是獵人\N{\fs13}They were hunters.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.82,1:48:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以韋恩家族會隕落\N{\fs13}So falls the house of Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.59,1:48:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得等待更多證據\N{\fs13}We gotta wait for more evidence,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.39,1:48:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但問題還在\N{\fs13}but the question still remains,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.36,1:48:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fs13}where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.23,1:48:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果超人沒有參與其中\N{\fs13}If superman was not involved,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.57,1:48:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他光明磊落 那為何自慘劇發生的那天起\N{\fs13}if he's got nothing to hide, then why hasn't he been seen
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.94,1:48:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一直沒看到他現身\N{\fs13}since the day of this tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.94,1:48:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能就這麼指向...\N{\fs13}You can't point a finger and...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.07,1:48:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒指 沃倫 十根手指在這呢 看見沒\N{\fs13}I'm not pointing anything, Warren. Look. Ten fingers, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.84,1:48:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有罪犯...\N{\fs13}If there is going to be a criminal...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.16,1:50:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,黑夜已至\N{\fs13}The night is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.90,1:50:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾下\N{\fs13}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.17,1:51:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是見過...\N{\fs13}Don't I know...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.30,1:52:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨就叫小露 穿便服時就叫露拉\N{\fs13}Plain lo in the morning. Lola in slacks.\N{\fs13}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.30,1:52:09.14,TOP,,0,0,0,,注:改自小說《洛麗塔》中的句子
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.37,1:52:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,露易絲·萊恩\N{\fs13}Lois Lane.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.78,1:52:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,來看看風景\N{\fs13}Mmm. Come see the view.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.11,1:52:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,高度的秘訣\N{\fs13}Now the secret to the height
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.32,1:52:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在於建築材料\N{\fs13}is the building material.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.62,1:52:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏用的是輕金屬 所以在風中有點晃\N{\fs13}It's light metals which sway a bit in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.79,1:52:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你對萊克斯集團的金屬也有些瞭解 對吧 萊恩小姐\N{\fs13}And you know something about lexcorp metals, don't you, miss Lane?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.13,1:52:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經查實了你的所作所為\N{\fs13}I've proven what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.00,1:52:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真能折騰\N{\fs13}Wow, you're feisty.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.10,1:52:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜 那一切都將隨風而逝\N{\fs13}Unfortunately, that will blow away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.60,1:52:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就如沙漠中的沙子\N{\fs13}Like sand in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.64,1:52:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個瘋子\N{\fs13}You're psychotic.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.77,1:52:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,狹隘的頭腦都是用\N{\fs13}That is a three-syllable word
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.24,1:52:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這個詞來描述偉大創想的\N{\fs13}for any thought too big for little minds.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.05,1:52:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,下個話題 圈圈\N{\fs13}Hmm. Next category: Circles.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.58,1:52:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他們找超人找了一圈一圈又一圈\N{\fs13}Round and round and round they go to find superman.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.35,1:52:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,搞錯話題了 少年 應該是三角形\N{\fs13}Wrong category, boy. No, no, triangles.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.49,1:52:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 歐幾里得的三角不等式\N{\fs13}Yes, euclid's triangle inequality.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.09,1:53:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,任意兩點之間的最短距離\N{\fs13}The shortest distance between any two points
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.29,1:53:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是直線\N{\fs13}is a straight path.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.09,1:53:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信通向超人最直的線\N{\fs13}And I believe the straightest path to superman
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.03,1:53:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是一條非常小的路...\N{\fs13}is a pretty little road...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.49,1:53:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,叫露易絲·萊恩\N{\fs13}Called Lois Lane.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.49,1:53:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你回來了\N{\fs13}You came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.79,1:53:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你回來了\N{\fs13}You came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.38,1:53:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 這裏有不少問題啊\N{\fs13}Boy, do we have problems up here!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.86,1:54:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,關於...\N{\fs13}The...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.65,1:54:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,關於世間邪惡的問題\N{\fs13}The problem of... Of evil in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.13,1:54:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,關於至善的問題\N{\fs13}The problem of absolute virtue.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.75,1:54:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會打殘你 但我要把你收監\N{\fs13}I'll take you in without breaking you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.92,1:54:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這更是你應得的\N{\fs13}Which is more than you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.30,1:54:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,關於你高高在上的問題\N{\fs13}The problem of you on top of everything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.19,1:54:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你凌駕於一切之上\N{\fs13}You above all.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.90,1:54:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因為神就是這樣\N{\fs13}Ah, because that's what god is.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.40,1:54:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,荷魯斯 阿波羅 耶和華 卡爾·艾爾\N{\fs13}Horus. Apollo. Jehovah. Kal- El.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.77,1:54:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克·約瑟夫·肯特\N{\fs13}Clark Joseph Kent.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.54,1:54:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 克拉克·喬 我們對神的稱呼取決於我們的部族\N{\fs13}See, what we call god depends upon our tribe, Clark-Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.75,1:54:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因為神也分部族 神也選立場\N{\fs13}Because god is tribal. God takes sides.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.88,1:54:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我小時候 天上可沒人來干涉\N{\fs13}No man in the sky intervened when I was a boy
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.88,1:54:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸的拳頭和憎惡 將我從中解救\N{\fs13}to deliver me from daddy's fist and abominations. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.92,1:54:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就明白了 如果神是全能的\N{\fs13}I figured out way back, if god is all-powerful,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.72,1:54:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那他就不可能至善至美\N{\fs13}he cannot be all-good.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.86,1:54:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他至善至美\N{\fs13}And if he is all-good,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.43,1:54:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那他就不可能全能\N{\fs13}then he cannot be all-powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.77,1:54:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而這兩者 你都不可能\N{\fs13}And neither can you be.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.05,1:54:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他們需要親眼看到\N{\fs13}They need to see the fraud you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.20,1:54:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你的假象\N{\fs13}With their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.77,1:55:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上的鮮血\N{\fs13}The blood on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.64,1:55:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹了什麼\N{\fs13}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.06,1:55:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚他們就會看到\N{\fs13}And tonight, they will.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.71,1:55:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我的朋友 因為你要去赴約\N{\fs13}Yes. Because you, my friend, have a date.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.88,1:55:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要飛越海灣\N{\fs13}Across the bay.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.49,1:55:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他積聚了兩年的恨意 是時候爆發了\N{\fs13}Ripe fruit, his hate. Two years growing.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.99,1:55:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不過逼他爆發 倒沒怎麼費力\N{\fs13}But it did not take much to push him over, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.99,1:55:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小紅字 大爆炸\N{\fs13}Little red notes, big bang.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.45,1:55:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你害死了你的家人\N{\fs13}You let your family die!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.29,1:55:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你要飛到他那裏\N{\fs13}And now you will fly to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.17,1:55:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,與他一戰\N{\fs13}And you will battle him.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.29,1:55:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,至死方休\N{\fs13}To the death.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.80,1:55:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,黑與藍 對決之夜\N{\fs13}Black and blue. Fight night!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.38,1:55:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,史上最偉大的角鬥士對決\N{\fs13}The greatest gladiator match in the history of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.80,1:55:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,天神對凡人\N{\fs13}God versus man.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.18,1:55:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,白晝對黑夜\N{\fs13}Day versus night.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.08,1:55:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,氪星之子對哥譚蝙蝠\N{\fs13}Son of Krypton versus bat of Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.15,1:55:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我會為了你 而與他一戰?\N{\fs13}You think I'll fight him for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.94,1:55:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我認為你會為了你生命中的\N{\fs13}Yes, I do. I think you will fight-fight-fight
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.19,1:55:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那位女神戰鬥 戰鬥 戰鬥\N{\fs13}for that special lady in your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.16,1:55:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她在地面很安全 而你呢\N{\fs13}She's safe on the ground. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.74,1:55:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,差點說對 但我說的不是露易絲\N{\fs13}Close, but I am not talking about Lois.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.10,1:56:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是她 每個男孩的女神都是他的母親\N{\fs13}No. Every boy's special lady is his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.29,1:56:03.92,TOP,,0,0,0,,女巫
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.33,1:56:06.49,TOP,,0,0,0,,女巫
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.17,1:56:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎 瑪莎 瑪莎\N{\fs13}Martha, Martha, Martha.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.65,1:56:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,飛天惡魔的母親一定是個女巫\N{\fs13}Why, the mother of a flying demon must be a witch.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.62,1:56:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對女巫的刑罰 是什麼來著\N{\fs13}The punishment for witches, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.49,1:56:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 被火燒死\N{\fs13}That's right. Death by fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.98,1:56:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fs13}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.23,1:56:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我不會讓他們告訴我\N{\fs13}I don't know! I would not let them tell me!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.95,1:56:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是殺了我 瑪莎就會死\N{\fs13}If you kill me, Martha dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.54,1:56:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你飛走 瑪莎也會死\N{\fs13}And if you fly away, mmm, Martha also dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.71,1:56:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但你要是殺了那蝙蝠...\N{\fs13}But if you kill the bat...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.71,1:56:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎就能活下來\N{\fs13}Martha lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.05,1:56:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這就對了\N{\fs13}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.84,1:56:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這就對了\N{\fs13}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.89,1:56:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,現在神都屈服於我的意志了\N{\fs13}And now god bends to my will.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.23,1:57:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,現在攝像機在你的飛船裏等待著\N{\fs13}Ooh, now the cameras are waiting at your ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.40,1:57:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等待著讓全世界看到神的缺陷\N{\fs13}For the world to see the holes in the holy.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.67,1:57:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 全能的神在需要之時\N{\fs13}Yes, the almighty comes clean
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.17,1:57:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,便會盡顯他的骯髒\N{\fs13}about how dirty he is when it counts.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.54,1:57:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想救瑪莎\N{\fs13}To save Martha,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.24,1:57:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就把蝙蝠的頭帶給我\N{\fs13}bring me the head of the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.71,1:57:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,聖母啊 你能看看時間嗎\N{\fs13}Mother of god, would you look at the time?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.58,1:57:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你到這裏時 還有一個小時\N{\fs13}When you came here, you had an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.19,1:57:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,現在更少了\N{\fs13}Now it's less.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.84,1:58:29.10,TOP,,0,0,0,,飛船墜毀點活動異常
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.75,1:58:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在現場的是布魯克·鮑德溫\N{\fs13}Brooke Baldwin is on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.45,1:58:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯克 你正在直播 你看到什麼了\N{\fs13}Brooke, you're live on the air. What are you seeing?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.69,1:58:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,飛船那邊有狀況\N{\fs13}There's something happening at the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.66,1:58:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它在發出大量能量波\N{\fs13}It's sending massive power surges.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.90,1:58:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,警方直升機正在該區域周圍盤旋\N{\fs13}Police helicopters surrounding the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.78,1:58:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在管制中心四周設了路障\N{\fs13}They've created a barricade around this containment center.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.03,1:58:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正試圖靠近一點\N{\fs13}And we're trying to get a little bit closer here
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.63,1:58:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,來搞清楚是怎麼回事\N{\fs13}to find out what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.33,1:58:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏混亂不堪 你們能看到那道閃電\N{\fs13}It is absolute chaos. You can see that lightning,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.34,1:58:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還有那些電波\N{\fs13}those surges of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.17,1:58:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,它們似乎每分鐘都在變得更為猛烈\N{\fs13}They seem to be getting stronger by the minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.27,1:58:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,去星球日報\N{\fs13}Daily planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.01,1:58:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,露易絲\N{\fs13}Lois.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.55,1:59:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須去哥譚 說服他幫助我\N{\fs13}I have to go to Gotham to convince him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.76,1:59:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,誰\N{\fs13}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.82,1:59:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,否則他就得死\N{\fs13}Or he has to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.85,1:59:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\N{\fs13}Clark.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.46,1:59:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這世上沒人能一直善良下去\N{\fs13}No one stays good in this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.57,1:59:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但截至目前 這座城市的大部分地區仍處於停電狀態\N{\fs13}But as of right now, much of the city remains in the dark tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.57,1:59:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼多混亂 那麼多讓人費解的事 都在今晚的大都會發生了\N{\fs13}Much chaos. Much confusing happening on the streets of Metropolis tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.91,1:59:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,直升機仍包圍著該區域\N{\fs13}Those helicopters are still surrounding the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.93,1:59:31.43,TOP,,0,0,0,,英雄公園活動異常
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.83,1:59:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你們能否看到那些閃電...\N{\fs13}I don't know if you can still see those bolts of lightning...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.55,1:59:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一則新消息 來自:布魯斯·韋恩\N男孩也會分享
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.71,1:59:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,破解了盧瑟的硬盤 發現了你的照片\N但那不屬於你
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.71,1:59:54.14,TOP,,0,0,0,,來自: 布魯斯·韋恩\N主題: 男孩也會分享
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.03,2:00:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.83,2:00:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.96,2:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你都去過哪
