Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.48,2:01:41.33,TOP,,0,0,0,,塞拉斯·斯通日誌分錄 實驗室 03\N臨床試驗 V-102 原型A1B-A  星際實驗室資料
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.47,2:01:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,2400小時又2分鐘 對像正在迅速衰弱\N{\fs13}2400 hours and 2 minutes. Subject declining rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.51,2:01:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所有程序上的干預手段都失敗了\N{\fs13}All procedural interventions have failed.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.44,2:01:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,結果\N{\fs13}Outcome
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.62,2:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,將是死亡\N{\fs13}will be death.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.56,2:02:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉斯·斯通醫生中止了所有臨床協議\N{\fs13}Dr. Silas stone suspending all clinical protocol.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.57,2:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,美國政府 對像6-19-82 已成功激活\N{\fs13}Us gov, object 6-19-82 is successfully activated.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.72,2:02:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要一架直升機去哥譚\N{\fs13}I need a chopper to Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.22,2:02:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,打電話給直升機場\N{\fs13}Call the heliport.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.05,2:02:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,直升機? 我們連自行車都快承擔不起了\N{\fs13}Chopper? We can barely afford a bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.35,2:02:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想追新聞?\N{\fs13}You wanna chase a story?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.36,2:02:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去飛船那\N{\fs13}Go to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.27,2:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,超人可能已經在那了\N{\fs13}Superman's probably there already.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.03,2:02:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,佩裏 這不是為了新聞\N{\fs13}Perry, it's not for a story.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.67,2:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,珍妮 給她弄一架直升機去哥譚\N{\fs13}Jenny, get her a chopper to Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.37,2:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,別停到停機坪 給我停到樓頂\N{\fs13}And forget the heliport. Put it on the goddamn roof.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.91,2:02:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,停到樓頂 露易絲\N{\fs13}On the roof, Lois!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:54.08,2:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去哪\N{\fs13}Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.75,2:02:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊\N{\fs13}There!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:12.93,2:03:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了\N{\fs13}Well, here I am.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.30,2:03:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯斯 別這樣\N{\fs13}Bruce. Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.44,2:03:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我錯了 你得聽我說\N{\fs13}I was wrong. You have to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.73,2:03:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯想要我們...\N{\fs13}Lex wants us to...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.96,2:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白\N{\fs13}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.30,2:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了\N{\fs13}There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.30,2:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs13}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.98,2:05:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,待著別動\N{\fs13}Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.55,2:05:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我動真格 你早就沒命了\N{\fs13}If I wanted it, you'd be dead already.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.05,2:05:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吸進去\N{\fs13}Breathe it in.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.42,2:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是恐懼\N{\fs13}That's fear.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.89,2:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你並不勇敢\N{\fs13}You're not brave.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.63,2:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,人類才勇敢\N{\fs13}Men are brave.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:09.19,2:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,監管之人 誰來監管
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.93,2:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我打賭你父母曾教導你說 你的存在是有意義的\N{\fs13}I bet your parents taught you that you mean something.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.60,2:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,說你來到這裏是有原因的\N{\fs13}That you're here for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.77,2:10:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而我父母教了我不同的一課\N{\fs13}My parents taught me a different lesson,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:02.88,2:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他們平白無故地\N{\fs13}dying in the gutter
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.95,2:10:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,死在了排水溝邊\N{\fs13}for no reason at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.70,2:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他們教導我 只有你逼迫這個世界\N{\fs13}They taught me the world only makes sense
Dialogue: 0,2:10:26.37,2:10:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,它才會變得合理\N{\fs13}if you force it to.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.24,2:11:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你從來都不是神\N{\fs13}You were never a god.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.44,2:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你甚至從來都不是人類\N{\fs13}You were never even a man.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.55,2:11:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在讓他殺掉瑪莎\N{\fs13}You're letting him kill Martha.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.56,2:11:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思\N{\fs13}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.57,2:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼提那個名字\N{\fs13}Why did you say that name?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.40,2:11:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他\N{\fs13}Find him.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.21,2:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,救出\N{\fs13}Save
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.91,2:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎\N{\fs13}Martha.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.54,2:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎\N{\fs13}Martha.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.94,2:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎·韋恩
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.74,2:12:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎\N{\fs13}Martha.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.85,2:12:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼提那個名字\N{\fs13}Why did you say that name?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.95,2:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎 你為什麼提那個名字\N{\fs13}Martha! Why did you say that name?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:28.79,2:12:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 住手\N{\fs13}Clark! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:30.09,2:12:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 住手\N{\fs13}Please! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.46,2:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼提那個名字\N{\fs13}Why did you say that name?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:33.13,2:12:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他母親的名字\N{\fs13}It's his mother's name!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.60,2:12:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他母親的名字\N{\fs13}It's his mother's name.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:09.46,2:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒得到任何答案\N{\fs13}We're not getting any answers.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:10.44,2:13:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們仍在管制中心外面\N{\fs13}We're still right outside the containment center.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.65,2:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,情況非常危險\N{\fs13}A dangerous situation.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:13.73,2:13:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,軍方和警員\N{\fs13}Military and police personnel
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.17,2:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正在包圍該區域\N{\fs13}surrounding the area.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.25,2:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,盧瑟\N{\fs13}Luthor.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:33.52,2:13:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要你的命來換她的命\N{\fs13}He wanted your life for hers.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.19,2:13:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她時間不多了\N{\fs13}She's losing time.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.03,2:13:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘偵查飛船似乎在吸取城市的電力\N{\fs13}The scout ship seems to be drawing power from the city.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:41.93,2:13:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是萊克斯干的\N{\fs13}It's got to be Lex.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.50,2:13:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,飛船那邊需要你 我會找到她的\N{\fs13}They need you at that ship. I'll find her.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.23,2:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我母親需要我 - 等等\N{\fs13}- My mother needs me. - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:49.44,2:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保證\N{\fs13}I'll make you a promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.87,2:13:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚瑪莎不會死\N{\fs13}Martha won't die tonight.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:20.87,2:14:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩老爺\N{\fs13}Master Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.24,2:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:23.47,2:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我偷聽了\N{\fs13}Uh, I'm sorry for listening in,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.24,2:14:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我追蹤俄國人的手機\N{\fs13}but I've tracked the Russian's phone
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.77,2:14:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,追蹤到了一間靠近港口的倉庫\N{\fs13}to a warehouse near the port.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:28.44,2:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,已幫你鎖定直飛路線\N{\fs13}You're locked onto it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.98,2:14:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不值得你這樣 阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}I don't deserve you, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:31.77,2:14:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 先生 你是不值得\N{\fs13}No, sir. You don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.13,2:14:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕要說再見了\N{\fs13}I'm afraid this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:58.60,2:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,注:改自雷蒙·錢德勒小說《漫長的告別》中的\N我們每說一次再見 你就離死亡更近了一點\N"To say goodbye is to die a little"\N{\fs13}And every time we say goodbye, you die a little.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:15.95,2:15:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把它打下來 - 打啊 快打\N{\fs13}- Take it down. - Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:41.11,2:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾弗雷德 你來操控\N{\fs13}You have to take it, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:43.64,2:15:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs13}Rght.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.02,2:15:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,開啟無人機模式\N{\fs13}Commencing drone mode.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.06,2:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,熱成像顯示\N{\fs13}Thermal imaging is showing me
Dialogue: 0,2:15:51.89,2:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,三樓有二十四個敵人\N{\fs13}two dozen hostiles on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:54.49,2:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不如我把你放在二樓吧\N{\fs13}Why don't I drop you off on the second?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:02.75,2:19:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,放下\N{\fs13}Drop it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.38,2:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了放下\N{\fs13}I said drop it!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:08.25,2:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我會殺了她\N{\fs13}I'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.42,2:19:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 我會動手的\N{\fs13}Believe me, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:16.53,2:19:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\fs13}I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:29.86,2:19:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了 我是你兒子的一個朋友\N{\fs13}It's okay. I'm a friend of your son's.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:33.08,2:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜到了 你也有披風\N{\fs13}I figured. The cape.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.08,2:20:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,遲到了 遲到了 小白兔說道\N{\fs13}"Late, late," says the white rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.08,2:20:06.56,TOP,,0,0,0,,注:改自《愛麗絲夢遊僊境》中總說自己遲到了的白兔的話
Dialogue: 0,2:20:05.61,2:20:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,離重生還有40秒\N{\fs13}40 seconds to animation.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:07.41,2:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對嗎 小白兔\N{\fs13}Right, wabbit?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:09.45,2:20:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒招了 也沒時間了\N{\fs13}Out of tricks, out of time.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:13.89,2:20:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,還少了蝙蝠的頭\N{\fs13}And one bat head short.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:16.39,2:20:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,離重生還有30秒\N{\fs13}30 seconds to animation.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:19.00,2:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,廚師來電了\N{\fs13} That'll be the cook.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:19.99,2:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪下\N{\fs13}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:21.29,2:20:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哥譚烤肉 全熟\N{\fs13}Gotham roast. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:24.10,2:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 爆壞消息吧\N{\fs13}Hello. Break the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.27,2:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我更想當面爆\N{\fs13}I'd rather do the breaking in person.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:29.17,2:20:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,離重生還有20秒\N{\fs13}20 seconds to animation.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.90,2:20:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你輸了\N{\fs13}You've lost.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.94,2:20:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎麼輸\N{\fs13}I don't know how to lose.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.47,2:20:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你會學會的\N{\fs13}You'll learn.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:35.34,2:20:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我會學會的\N{\fs13}I'll learn.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:36.98,2:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不恨罪惡之人\N{\fs13}I don't hate the sinner.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:39.48,2:20:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我恨的是罪惡本身 - 離重生還有10秒\N{\fs13}- I hate the sin. - 10 seconds to animation.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:41.89,2:20:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而你的罪惡 我的朋友 就是你的存在\N{\fs13}And yours, my friend, is existing.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.08,2:20:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能讓你贏\N{\fs13}I cannot let you win.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.44,2:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我給了那蝙蝠一戰的機會\N{\fs13}I gave the bat a fighting chance to do it,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:47.95,2:20:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不夠強\N{\fs13}but he was not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.02,2:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 如果凡人殺不了天神\N{\fs13}So, if man won't kill god...
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.02,2:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,二 一\N{\fs13}...two, one.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:54.86,2:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那就讓魔鬼代勞吧\N{\fs13}...the devil will do it!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.34,2:21:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,佩裏\N{\fs13}Perry!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:14.11,2:21:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 各位保持冷靜\N{\fs13}All right. Stay calm, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:16.63,2:21:18.59,TOP,,0,0,0,,大都會陷入一片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,2:21:16.78,2:21:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們收到報告稱這座城市\N{\fs13}We're getting reports there are total blackouts
Dialogue: 0,2:21:18.22,2:21:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,從北部到西北部都完全停電了\N{\fs13}in the north and to the northwest of the city.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:20.99,2:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,聯邦政府正在試圖查明\N{\fs13}Federal authorities are trying to determine
Dialogue: 0,2:21:22.23,2:21:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這是否是一次大規模恐怖襲擊的一部分\N{\fs13}if this is part of a larger terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:29.06,2:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,古老的氪星畸形生物\N{\fs13}Ancient Kryptonian deformity.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:33.03,2:21:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吾血之血\N{\fs13} Blood of my blood.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.41,2:21:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,生來就為了毀滅你\N{\fs13}Born to destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:47.31,2:21:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你的毀滅日\N{\fs13}Your doomsday.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:12.50,2:22:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 神死定了\N{\fs13}Now god is good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:40.93,2:23:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,總統來電了\N{\fs13}Potus joining.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.33,2:23:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,總統先生\N{\fs13}Mr. president.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:43.70,2:23:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼東西 卡爾文\N{\fs13}What the hell is it, Calvin?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:44.87,2:23:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這些是來自大都會市中心萊克斯集團\N{\fs13}These are live images from the top
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.37,2:23:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,塔樓樓頂的直播畫面\N{\fs13}of the lexcorp tower in downtown Metropolis.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.14,2:23:50.94,TOP,,0,0,0,,未知生物正在攻擊
Dialogue: 0,2:23:49.27,2:23:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,軍機正在趕往現場\N{\fs13}Military aircraft are on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:03.02,2:24:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你受傷了嗎 女士 - 我沒事\N{\fs13}- Are you hurt, ma'am? - I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:04.98,2:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好  你會沒事的 好嗎\N{\fs13}Good. You're gonna be all right, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:16.53,2:24:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這個東西就在幾分鐘前\N{\fs13}This thing emerged from the Kryptonian
Dialogue: 0,2:24:18.90,2:24:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,從氪星飛船墜毀點出現了\N{\fs13}crash site just moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:21.20,2:24:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不過幸好市中心核心區的人都下班了\N{\fs13}Thankfully though, the work day is over in the downtown core.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:24.45,2:24:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏幾乎沒人了\N{\fs13}It's nearly empty.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.74,2:24:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,現在那些軍機 阿帕奇直升機\N{\fs13}Now military aircraft. Those are apache helicopters.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:29.48,2:24:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛抵達 畫面...\N{\fs13}They have now just arrived. The images that...
Dialogue: 0,2:25:06.41,2:25:08.53,TOP,,0,0,0,,軍隊與某種生物發生交戰
Dialogue: 0,2:25:08.21,2:25:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們...我們剛與大都會8台新聞失去了通訊連接\N{\fs13}We've, uh... We just lost connection with Metropolis 8 news.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:11.42,2:25:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不清楚那裏發生了什麼\N{\fs13}Now, it's not clear what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:17.36,2:25:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊怎麼了 阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}What's happening there, Alfred?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.76,2:25:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說好呢\N{\fs13}How best to describe it?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:22.73,2:25:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會空域已被暫時關閉\N{\fs13}Metropolis airspace has been closed briefly.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.63,2:25:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能打擾下嗎\N{\fs13}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:25.51,2:25:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們懇請您待在座位上\N{\fs13}We kindly ask that you stay in your seats.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:26.60,2:25:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我能打擾下嗎\N{\fs13}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.27,2:25:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,普林斯小姐\N{\fs13}Miss prince?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:44.12,2:25:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,長官 看 他們已離開城市\N{\fs13}Sir. Look, they've cleared the city.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:46.12,2:25:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像在把它帶入太空\N{\fs13}Looks like he's taking it into space.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:47.79,2:25:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能直接動用核武器了 總統先生\N{\fs13}We can go straight to key red, Mr. president.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:49.62,2:25:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,還不行 你瘋了嗎\N{\fs13}Not yet. Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:50.85,2:25:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他們夠高了 能用核彈攻擊他們\N{\fs13}They're high enough that we can nuke 'em
Dialogue: 0,2:25:52.71,2:25:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有一人傷亡 長官\N{\fs13}with no casualties, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:53.93,2:25:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,會有一人 總統先生 超人\N{\fs13}One casualty, Mr. president. Superman.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:59.43,2:26:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,願上帝寬恕我們所有人\N{\fs13}God have mercy on us all.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:07.14,2:26:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 已插入鑰匙 - 已插入鑰匙\N{\fs13}- Key is hot. - Key is hot.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.72,2:26:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,紅鳥已就位 等待發射 長官\N{\fs13}Red birds are armed to deploy, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:12.48,2:26:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,發射吧\N{\fs13}Fire at will.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:13.78,2:26:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,三 二 一\N{\fs13}Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.83,2:27:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs13}Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:28.68,2:27:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一號拋體 撞擊了\N{\fs13}Projectile 1. Impact.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:30.06,2:27:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大都會東部  斯特瑞克之島\N{\fs13}Stryker's island, east of Metropolis.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:31.76,2:27:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏無人居住\N{\fs13}That's uninhabited.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:33.06,2:27:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,二號拋體\N{\fs13}Projectile 2...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:40.17,2:27:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,無重返大氣層跡象\N{\fs13}No apparent reentry.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:42.37,2:27:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,二號拋體?\N{\fs13}Projectile 2?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:44.34,2:27:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,超人 總統先生 二號拋體是超人\N{\fs13}Superman, Mr. president. Projectile 2 was superman.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:50.18,2:27:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,長官\N{\fs13}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:52.49,2:27:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,它在移動\N{\fs13}It's moving.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:34.75,2:28:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,衝擊波越來越強了\N{\fs13}The shockwaves are getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:36.46,2:28:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們每擊中它一次 都會讓它變得更強\N{\fs13}Every time we hit it, we make it more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:39.63,2:28:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不能攻擊\N{\fs13}We can't attack.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:42.29,2:28:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,卡爾文 你在說什麼\N{\fs13}What are you saying, Calvin?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:44.76,2:28:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我在說它是殺不死的\N{\fs13}I'm saying it's unkillable.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:14.82,2:29:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩老爺 聽得到嗎\N{\fs13}Master Wayne, are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:16.83,2:29:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾弗雷德\N{\fs13}Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:18.00,2:29:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它是氪星生物\N{\fs13}It's Kryptonian.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:19.83,2:29:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只有氪石武器才能殺死它\N{\fs13}Only kryptonite weapons can kill it.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:22.54,2:29:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也許吧 如果你有剩餘的話\N{\fs13}They might. If you had any left.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.00,2:29:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我還剩一發氪石彈\N{\fs13}I got one round left.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:29.18,2:29:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那根矛 阿爾弗雷德 那根矛 是純氪石做的\N{\fs13}The spear. Alfred, the spear. It's pure kryptonite.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:33.35,2:29:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,落在哥譚了\N{\fs13}It's back in Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:34.53,2:29:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能刺穿它的皮膚 那根矛就能殺死它\N{\fs13}If I can penetrate the skin, the spear will kill it.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:37.98,2:29:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,理論上是這樣\N{\fs13}It would in theory.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.35,2:29:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我得引它追著我回到哥譚\N{\fs13}I've gotta get it to chase me back to the city.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:42.15,2:29:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,回到氪石那裏\N{\fs13}Back to the kryptonite.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:44.55,2:30:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,見鬼\N{\fs13}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:35.71,2:31:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼把它帶回這座城市\N{\fs13}Why did you bring him back to the city?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:37.64,2:31:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這個港口已經被廢棄了\N{\fs13}The port is abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:39.14,2:31:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏有能殺死它的武器\N{\fs13}There's a weapon here that can kill it.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:53.58,2:31:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到那根矛了嗎\N{\fs13}Did you find the spear?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:55.82,2:31:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點忙\N{\fs13}I've been a little busy.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:57.24,2:32:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這個東西 這個生物 似乎是靠吸收能量活著的\N{\fs13}This thing, this creature, seems to feed on energy.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:02.70,2:32:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這個東西來自另一個世界\N{\fs13}This thing is from another world.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:06.79,2:32:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的世界\N{\fs13}My world.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:07.87,2:32:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前殺過來自其他世界的東西\N{\fs13}I've killed things from other worlds before.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:12.54,2:32:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟你一夥的嗎\N{\fs13}Is she with you?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:14.34,2:32:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為她跟你一夥的\N{\fs13}I thought she was with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:54.69,2:35:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\N{\fs13}Clark!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:05.07,2:36:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\N{\fs13}Clark!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:16.62,2:36:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\N{\fs13}Clark!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:18.52,2:36:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 你沒事吧\N{\fs13}Clark! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:57.96,2:36:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你\N{\fs13}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:03.29,2:37:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行 克拉克 你不能去\N{\fs13}No. No, Clark, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:08.47,2:37:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏是我的世界\N{\fs13}This is my world.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:10.40,2:37:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 克拉克 別去\N{\fs13}No, Clark, don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:15.47,2:37:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是我的世界\N{\fs13}You are my world.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:17.84,2:37:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:22.15,2:37:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 克拉克\N{\fs13}Please. Clark!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:39.24,2:42:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,星球日報  超人已死\N恐懼之夜 失落之晨
Dialogue: 0,2:42:43.88,2:42:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,星球日報記者克拉克·肯特\N在報道哥譚一役中遇害
Dialogue: 0,2:42:46.22,2:42:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,萊克斯·盧瑟因涉嫌國會大廈炸彈襲擊被捕
Dialogue: 0,2:43:06.35,2:43:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哈里的\N三明治店
Dialogue: 0,2:43:12.36,2:43:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,肯尼迪已死
Dialogue: 0,2:44:29.84,2:44:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs13}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:37.92,2:44:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克之前把這個寄了過來 想給你個驚喜\N{\fs13}Clark had this sent here, so he could surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:07.73,2:47:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,死者要復活\N{\fs13}"The dead shall live.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:07.73,2:47:14.11,TOP,,0,0,0,,注:出自《以賽亞書》第26章19節
Dialogue: 0,2:47:10.73,2:47:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,屍首要興起\N{\fs13}"My slain shall rise again.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:16.94,2:47:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,睡在塵埃的啊 要醒起歌唱\N{\fs13}"Awake and sing, ye that dwell in dust.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:21.25,2:47:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因你的甘露好像菜蔬上的甘露\N{\fs13}"For thy dew is like the dew of morning.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:26.42,2:47:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,地也要交出死人來\N{\fs13}"And the earth shall give birth to her dead."
Dialogue: 0,2:47:39.30,2:47:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要搭車回家一趟\N{\fs13} I need a ride back to the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:41.43,2:47:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘帶支票本了 還要付錢給殯葬承辦人呢\N{\fs13}I forgot my checkbook to pay the funeral director.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:44.14,2:47:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說全都付清了\N{\fs13}They said it's all taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:46.27,2:47:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,誰付的\N{\fs13}By whom?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:48.27,2:47:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,匿名捐贈者\N{\fs13}Anonymous donor.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:33.82,2:48:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,東邊的那些表演只是在下葬一副空棺材\N{\fs13}All those circuses back east burying an empty box.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:37.99,2:48:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不知道如何緬懷他\N{\fs13}They don't know how to honor him,
Dialogue: 0,2:48:41.09,2:48:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只能當做軍人\N{\fs13}except as a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:44.66,2:48:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他活著時\N{\fs13}I've failed him
Dialogue: 0,2:48:46.61,2:48:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我辜負了他\N{\fs13}in life.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:49.47,2:48:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他死後 我不會再辜負他\N{\fs13}I won't fail him in death.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:53.27,2:48:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我找到其他像你這樣的人\N{\fs13}Help me find the others like you.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:55.94,2:48:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也許他們不希望被找到\N{\fs13}Perhaps they don't want to be found.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:58.81,2:49:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會的 他們還要戰鬥\N{\fs13}They will. And they'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:02.81,2:49:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須聯手\N{\fs13}We have to stand together.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:12.52,2:49:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一百年前 我離開了人類\N{\fs13}100 years ago, I walked away from mankind.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:17.83,2:49:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,遠離了一個世紀的恐怖萬象\N{\fs13}From a century of horrors.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:23.37,2:49:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,人類創造了一個不可能聯手的世界\N{\fs13}Man made a world where standing together is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:30.14,2:49:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,人類依然優秀\N{\fs13}Men are still good.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:34.54,2:49:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們爭鬥 廝殺\N{\fs13}We fight. We kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:38.65,2:49:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們相互背叛\N{\fs13}We betray one another.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:42.92,2:49:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們能重整旗鼓\N{\fs13}But we can rebuild.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:46.22,2:49:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能做得更好\N{\fs13}We can do better.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:49.36,2:49:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會的\N{\fs13}We will.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:51.40,2:49:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須如此\N{\fs13}We have to.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:09.86,2:50:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在尋找他的豐碑\N看看你的周圍吧
Dialogue: 0,2:50:15.69,2:50:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,其他像我一樣的人\N{\fs13}The others like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:17.26,2:50:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你說他們必須戰鬥\N{\fs13}Why did you say they'll have to fight?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:24.93,2:50:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一種感覺\N{\fs13}Just a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:38.38,2:50:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,囚犯 A-C-23-19-40\N{\fs13}Prisoner A-C-23-19-40.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:40.98,2:50:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,監獄長想跟你談話 站起來\N{\fs13}The warden wants to speak to you, so stand to your feet.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:45.32,2:50:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我再說一遍\N{\fs13}I'm gonna say this one more time.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:47.22,2:50:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,監獄長想跟你談話 站起來\N{\fs13}The warden wants to speak to you, so stand to your feet.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:57.89,2:50:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,轉過身 面朝牆\N{\fs13}Turn around and face the wall.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:01.83,2:51:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,前額靠住牆\N{\fs13}Place your forehead against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:04.24,2:51:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,雙手放背後\N{\fs13}Put your hands behind your back,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:06.14,2:51:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我進來好銬住你\N{\fs13}so that I can come in and restrain you.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:36.50,2:51:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,無論你做什麼 無論你去哪裏\N{\fs13}Whatever you do, wherever you go,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:39.44,2:51:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我都會盯著你\N{\fs13}I'll be watching you.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:45.01,2:51:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我們啊\N{\fs13}Look at us.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:47.68,2:51:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一切就是這樣分崩離析的\N{\fs13}This is how it all caves in.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:49.98,2:51:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,韋恩莊園的文明被丟棄了\N{\fs13}Civilization on the Wayne manor's out the window.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:59.46,2:52:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是誰會相信我呢 我...\N{\fs13}But who would believe me? I...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:02.36,2:52:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我瘋了\N{\fs13}I'm insane.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:06.06,2:52:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我都沒法受審\N{\fs13}I'm not even fit to stand trial.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:08.23,2:52:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fs13}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:10.17,2:52:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,悉心照料精神病患者的醫院有不少\N{\fs13}We have hospitals that treat the mentally ill with compassion.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:15.31,2:52:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但那裏不是你要去的地方\N{\fs13}But that's not where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:17.31,2:52:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我已給你安排好轉去哥譚的阿卡姆瘋人院\N{\fs13}I arranged for you to get transferred to arkham asylum in Gotham.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:22.21,2:52:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那裏還有些朋友\N{\fs13}I still have some friends there.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:24.75,2:52:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在等著你\N{\fs13}They're expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:30.89,2:52:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但鐘聲已被敲響\N{\fs13}But the bell's already been rung.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:37.59,2:52:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他們已經聽到了\N{\fs13}And they've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:40.90,2:52:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在黑暗之中\N{\fs13}Out in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:42.67,2:52:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在群星之間\N{\fs13}Among the stars.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:48.41,2:52:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,叮咚 神已經死了\N{\fs13}Ding dong, the god is dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:48.41,2:52:51.97,TOP,,0,0,0,,注:改自1939年版《綠野僊蹤》插曲《Ding-Dong!The Witch Is Dead》
Dialogue: 0,2:53:01.35,2:53:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但鐘聲是收不回的\N{\fs13}But a bell cannot be unrung!
Dialogue: 0,2:53:05.46,2:53:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他餓了\N{\fs13}He's hungry.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:07.59,2:53:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他找到我們了\N{\fs13} He's found us.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:10.19,2:53:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他要來了\N{\fs13}And he's coming!


